desc=I have a request for you. I look for some fur to use in this winter. I'm likely to catch a cold because of the heavy work. The fur should be warm. There are  Wild Boars here in Weedridge. After collecting Wild Boar's fur, I'll take it to Kyra. She'll make me a warm fur coat. Ha ha, I'm already excited.
runDlg=Isn't this finished yet?? I want to put it on as soon as possible
finishDlg=Oh!  This is good of quality. Thanks.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Wild Boar's fur collection
desc=I have a request to you. I look for some fur to use in this winter. Leader is likely to catch cold because of heavy work. The fur should be warm.  There are  Wild Boars here Weedridge. After collecting  Wild Boar's fur, I'll take the fur to Kyra. Then she'll give me a warm fur coat. Ha ha, I'm already excited.
