</newversion></questtextxml></nwarri007><nexp007><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Hunting Wild Boar 
desc=Ah, you're coming right in time. We have a little request. Wild Boars are increasing in Weedridge. They're a holy terror. These Wild Boars destroy structures and harass people continously.  We are also villagers same as the others, so I want you to help. Go eliminate Wild Boars.
runDlg=Isn't it finished yet? This is nothing that can wait. 
finishDlg=Good job. I'll give you a reward. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunting Wild Boar 
desc=Ah, you came in time when we are going to request. Wild Boars are increasing in Weedridge. They're a holy terror. These Wild Boars destroy structures and harass people repeatedly.  We are also same villagers, so I want you to help. Go eliminate Wild Boars.
runDlg=Isn't it finished yet? This is nothing to take time. 
finishDlg=Good job. I'll give you the reward. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nexp007><nexp008><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Collecting Tough Wild Boar's Tooth 
desc=Um..well, may I ask you for a favour? There is some stuff, I want to get. So I asked Mark but he refused, saying he is busy. I hope, you can bring me the stuff. That is Tough Wild Boar's Tooth. I have a plan for decorating with these after collecting. Please, bring me Tough Wild Boar's teeth.
runDlg=Um? Not yet? I'll give you a reward for your effort. 
finishDlg=Thank you. I did never expect Mark to refuse!  Why do men ignore women's mind? 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collecting Tough Wild Boar's tooth 
desc=Um..well, may I ask you this request? There are some stuff I want to get. So I asked Mark but he refused, saying he was busy. I hope you bring the stuff. That is Tough Wild Boar's tooth. I have a plan that decorates these after collecting. Please, bring Tough Wild Boar's teeth.
runDlg=Um? Not yet? I'll give a reward as your effort. 
finishDlg=Thank you. I do never expect Mark's refusal!  Why do men ignore women's mind? 
</newversion></questtextxml></nexp008><nexp009><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Hunting Devil Walker  
desc=There is an evil group called Devil Walker in Demon Valley at the northwest of Weedridge. They harm passersby and rob them of goods for trade. I heard about your remarkable activities from Kyra. So I believe you'll deal with this mission well. Go eliminate Devil Walkers. Of course, there will be an adequate reward. 
runDlg=Without eliminating the Devil Walkers, traders can never transport their goods safely. 
finishDlg=Good job. Indeed, you deserve to be praised by Kyra. Here is your reward. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunting Devil Walker  
desc=There is a group of evil called Devil Walker in Demon Valley at the northwest of Weedridge. They harm passersby and rob of goods for trade. I heard about your remarkable activities from Kyra. So I believe you'll deal with this mission well. Go eliminate Devil Walkers. Of course, the reward will be enough. 
runDlg=Without eliminating Devil Walkers, traders could never transport goods safely. 
