</newversion></questtextxml></nexp009><nsoula007><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Collecting Wild Boar's Essence
desc= We, the Divine Association, continue to investigate about Weedridge. Your job is to collect Wild Boar's essence this time. After collecting as much as possible of this essence, we'll draw a conclusion what happened. Go collect the essence and bring it to me as soon as possible. May the Spirits bless you all the time. 
runDlg=Did you get all the essence? 
finishDlg=You brought a lot of essence. Good job. I'll let you know the next step right now. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collecting Wild Boar's essence
desc= We Divine Association continue to investigate about Weedridge. Your job is to collect Wild Boar's essence this time. After collecting the maxium of essence, we'll draw a conclusion what happened. Go collect the essence and bring me as soon as possible. May Spirits bless you all the time. 
runDlg=Did you bring all the essence? 
finishDlg=You brought a lot of essence. Good job. I'll let you know next job right now. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula007><nsoula008><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Eliminating Tough Wild Boar 
desc=The next mission is eliminating Tough Wild Boar. As a result of my investigation, I knew, it's too late to change them into kind creatures. It's very serious that  they attack villagers. So we, the Divine Association, decided to eliminate Tough Wild Boar. I give you this mission. With the Spirits' blessing and in the name of Divine Association, eliminate the Tough Wild Boars. 
runDlg=This needs to be doen in order to be in harmony with all creatures.
finishDlg=I'm pleased you finished so well. There seems to be a reason they get violent. The Divine Association will investigate this reason. Good job.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Eliminating Tough Wild Boar 
desc=Next mission is eliminating Tough Wild Boar. As a result of my investigation, I knew, it's too late to change them into good stuff. More serious thing is what  they attack villagers. So we Divine Association decided to eliminate Tough Wild Boar. I give you this mission. With Spirits' blessing and the name of Divine Association, eliminate the Tough Wild Boars. 
runDlg=Nothing can be done now for the harmony with other creatures.
finishDlg=I'm pleased you did. There seems to be a reason they get violent. Divine Association will investigate the reason. Good job.
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula008><nsoula009><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Hunting Devil Walker 
desc=There is a place named Demon Valley in the northeast of Weedridge. It says that the devil, that the Divine Association has investigated these days, is living there. The chief of the village, Mark, has longed to eliminate the Devil Walker long before. It's natural he dislikes the devil harassing villagers. So we also plan to give our suppirt as a favor to this village. Go to Demon Valley and eliminate Devil Walker. And after that, go to Mark. 
runDlg=Did you eliminate all Devil Walkers? They are just disrupters of nature. we also want them to disappear. 
finishDlg=Eliminating what isn't natural is a nice thing from our point of view.  Thanks to you, Cardiff Island recovers its true self.  So I'm really happy. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunting Devil Walker 
desc=There is a place named Demon Valley in the northeast of Weedridge. It says that the devil that Divine Association has investigated in these days is living in there. The chief of village, Mark, has longed to eliminate the Devil Walker since long before. It's natural he dislike the devil harassing villagers. So we also plan to help with gratitude in favor of this village. Go to Demon Valley and eliminate Devil Walker. And after that, go to Mark. 
runDlg=Did you eliminate all of Devil Walkers? They are just disrupters of nature we also want to disappear. 
finishDlg=Eliminating what isn't nature is a nice thing in our stance.  Thank to you, Cardiff Island recovers its true self.  So I'm really happy. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula009><nnobi008><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Elimination of Devil Walker 
desc=It's time to eliminate the disrupters of Weedridge. The lord declared a war against Devil Walkers, the disrupters of Weedridge. So we nobles gave a firm promise about joining the lord and following his will. There is Demon Valley in the northwest of Weedridge. The Devil Walker are living there. Go eliminate Devil Walkers. 
runDlg=Please, you must help the village and the lord. The Battle with this group of Devil Walker seems to be a hard fight, but it's not. 
