desc=There is another thing you have to help with. Zombies in the cave began to counterattack our attacks. They have no intelligence, but they continue to attack intelligently. Go ahead and get rid of these Zombies. 
runDlg=I order you to wipe out the Zombies. Clean up all the Zombies in the cave. 
finishDlg=I believe there will be no Zombie attacks any more. There is another job, please wait for a while.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Whisman Zombie Elimination 
Mission2=Hagdis Zombie Elimination 
