runDlg=I order you to wipe out Zombie. Clean up all the Zombies in the cave. 
finishDlg=I believe there seems to be no Zombie's attack any more. You have a next mission, please wait for a while.
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10019><ad3b10020><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Whisman Ghoul Elimination 
Mission2=Hagdis Ghoul Elimination 
desc=There was another group who have attacked us along with the Zombies. Their name is Ghoul. Only pieces of rotten meat and bones but they hit people with terror. But you don't need to be afraid of them. Aren't you the veteran who has overcome many difficulties? Go eliminate Ghouls. The time has come to seal this cursed place.
runDlg=Did you eliminate Ghouls? Come on, don't you want to take a rest after this job? 
finishDlg=You eliminated the Ghouls very well. Take a rest before carrying out another mission.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Whisman Ghoul Elimination 
Mission2=Hagdis Ghoul Elimination 
