</newversion></questtextxml></topbag019><nwarri007><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Wild Boar'un Postunu Toplam
desc=Senin i&#xE7;in bir g&#xF6;revim var. K&#x131;&#x15F;&#x131;n kullanmak &#xFC;zere biraz posta ihtiyac&#x131;m var. A&#x11F;&#x131;r &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;t&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;m i&#xE7;in &#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;tt&#xFC;m san&#x131;yorum. K&#xFC;rk beni s&#x131;cak tutacakt&#x131;r. Burada, yani Weedridge'de Wild Boar'lar var. Wild Boar'un postlar&#x131;n&#x131; toplad&#x131;ktan sonra Kyra'ya g&#xF6;t&#xFC;r. O bana bundan s&#x131;cak tutacak bir k&#xFC;rk yapacakt&#x131;r. Ha ha, &#x15F;imdiden heyecanland&#x131;m.
runDlg=Daha bitmedi mi?? Hadi, bir an &#xF6;nce giymek istiyorum
finishDlg=Oh! Bu &#xE7;ok kaliteli olmu&#x15F;. Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Wild Boar's fur collection
desc=I have a request to you. I look for some fur to use in this winter. Leader is likely to catch cold because of heavy work. The fur should be warm.  There are  Wild Boars here Weedridge. After collecting  Wild Boar's fur, I'll take the fur to Kyra. Then she'll give me a warm fur coat. Ha ha, I'm already excited.
runDlg=Isn't this finished yet?? I want to put on as soon as possible
finishDlg=Oh!  This is good of quality.
</newversion></questtextxml></nwarri007><nexp007><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Wild Boar av&#x131;
desc=Ah, tam da zaman&#x131;nda geldin. Ufak bir g&#xF6;revimiz olacak. Weedridge'deki Wild Boar'lar &#xE7;o&#x11F;al&#x131;yor. Tamamen ter&#xF6;r olu&#x15F;turuyorlar. Bu Wild Boar'lar yap&#x131;lara zarar veriyor ve insanlar&#x131; da devaml&#x131; taciz ediyorlar. Aynen di&#x11F;erleri gibi ,bizler de k&#xF6;yl&#xFC;y&#xFC;z, i&#x15F;te bu y&#xFC;zden yard&#x131;m&#x131;n&#x131; istiyorum. Git ve Wild Boar'lar&#x131; yok et.
runDlg=Daha bitmedi mi? Bu, bekleyecek bir i&#x15F; de&#x11F;il. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Sana bir &#xF6;d&#xFC;l verece&#x11F;im. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunting Wild Boar 
desc=Ah, you came in time when we are going to request. Wild Boars are increasing in Weedridge. They're a holy terror. These Wild Boars destroy structures and harass people repeatedly.  We are also same villagers, so I want you to help. Go eliminate Wild Boars.
runDlg=Isn't it finished yet? This is nothing to take time. 
finishDlg=Good job. I'll give you the reward. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nexp007><nexp008><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Tough Wild Boar'un Di&#x15F;ini Toplama 
desc=Um... &#x15F;ey, senden bir iyilik daha isteyebilir miyim? Almak istedi&#x11F;im bir &#x15F;eyler var. Mark'a sordum ama me&#x15F;gul oldu&#x11F;unu s&#xF6;yledi ve beni geri &#xE7;evirdi. Umar&#x131;m istedi&#x11F;im &#x15F;eyleri sen getirebilirsin. Tough Wild Boar'un Di&#x15F;i'nden bahsediyorum. Toplad&#x131;ktan sonra bunlar&#x131; dekorasyonda kullanmak istiyorum. L&#xFC;tfen, bana Tough Wild Boar'un di&#x15F;lerini getir.
runDlg=Um? Hen&#xFC;z de&#x11F;il mi? G&#xF6;sterdi&#x11F;in &#xE7;abaya kar&#x15F;&#x131;l&#x131;k sana bir hediye verece&#x11F;im. 
finishDlg=Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. Mark'&#x131;n geri &#xE7;evirece&#x11F;ini hi&#xE7; d&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;nmemi&#x15F;tim!  Erkekler neden kad&#x131;n akl&#x131;n&#x131; g&#xF6;rmezden gelir ki? 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collecting Tough Wild Boar's tooth 
desc=Um..well, may I ask you this request? There are some stuff I want to get. So I asked Mark but he refused, saying he was busy. I hope you bring the stuff. That is Tough Wild Boar's tooth. I have a plan that decorates these after collecting. Please, bring Tough Wild Boar's teeth.
runDlg=Um? Not yet? I'll give a reward as your effort. 
finishDlg=Thank you. I do never expect Mark's refusal!  Why do men ignore women's mind? 
</newversion></questtextxml></nexp008><nexp009><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Devil Walker Av&#x131; 
desc=Weedridge'in kuzeybat&#x131;s&#x131;ndaki Demon Valley'de (&#x15E;eytan Vadisi) Devil Walker denilen k&#xF6;t&#xFC;c&#xFC;l bir topluluk var. Yoldan ge&#xE7;enleri taciz ediyorlar ve onlar&#x131;n ticari mallar&#x131;n&#x131; &#xE7;al&#x131;yorlar. Kyra'dan senin ba&#x15F;ar&#x131;lar&#x131;n hakk&#x131;nda &#xE7;ok &#x15F;ey duydum. Bu g&#xF6;revin de alt&#x131;ndan ba&#x15F;ar&#x131;yla kalkaca&#x11F;&#x131;na inan&#x131;yorum. Git ve Devil Walker'lar&#x131; yok et. Kar&#x15F;&#x131;l&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;nda elbette buna uygun bir &#xF6;d&#xFC;l de alacaks&#x131;n. 
runDlg=Devil Walker'lar yok edilmezse t&#xFC;ccarlar mallar&#x131;n&#x131; g&#xFC;venli bir &#x15F;ekilde ta&#x15F;&#x131;yamayacaklar. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Kyra'n&#x131;n dedi&#x11F;i kadar varm&#x131;&#x15F;s&#x131;n, &#xF6;vg&#xFC;y&#xFC; hak ediyorsun. &#x130;&#x15F;te &#xF6;d&#xFC;l&#xFC;n. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunting Devil Walker  
desc=There is a group of evil called Devil Walker in Demon Valley at the northwest of Weedridge. They harm passersby and rob of goods for trade. I heard about your remarkable activities from Kyra. So I believe you'll deal with this mission well. Go eliminate Devil Walkers. Of course, the reward will be enough. 
runDlg=Without eliminating Devil Walkers, traders could never transport goods safely. 
finishDlg=Good job. Indeed, you deserve to be praised from Kyra. Here is your reward. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nexp009><nsoula007><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Wild Boar'un &#xD6;z&#xFC;n&#xFC; toplama
desc=Bizler, yani Divine Association, Weedridge'i ara&#x15F;t&#x131;rmaya devam ediyoruz. K22Senin g&#xF6;revin ise bu kez Wild Boar'un &#xF6;z&#xFC;n&#xFC; toplamak. Bu &#xF6;zden m&#xFC;mk&#xFC;n oldu&#x11F;unca &#xE7;ok toplad&#x131;ktan sonra ne oldu&#x11F;una dair bir sonuca varmaya &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;aca&#x11F;&#x131;z. Git ve &#xF6;z&#xFC; topla, sonra da olabildi&#x11F;ince h&#x131;zl&#x131; bir &#x15F;ekjilde bana getir. Ruhlar seni kutsas&#x131;n. 
runDlg=&#xD6;z&#xFC; alabildin mi? 
finishDlg=&#xC7;ok fazla getirmi&#x15F;sin. &#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Bir sonraki ad&#x131;m&#x131; sana hemen bildirece&#x11F;im. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collecting Wild Boar's essence
desc= We Divine Association continue to investigate about Weedridge. Your job is to collect Wild Boar's essence this time. After collecting the maxium of essence, we'll draw a conclusion what happened. Go collect the essence and bring me as soon as possible. May Spirits bless you all the time. 
runDlg=Did you bring all the essence? 
finishDlg=You brought a lot of essence. Good job. I'll let you know next job right now. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula007><nsoula008><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Tough Wild Boar'u Yok etme 
desc=Bir sonraki g&#xF6;rev Tough Wild Boar'u yok etmek. Ara&#x15F;t&#x131;rmalar&#x131;m&#x131;n sonunda anlad&#x131;m ki bunlar&#x131; do&#x11F;ru d&#xFC;zg&#xFC;n yarat&#x131;klara d&#xF6;n&#xFC;&#x15F;t&#xFC;rmek i&#xE7;in art&#x131;k &#xE7;ok ge&#xE7;. K&#xF6;yl&#xFC;lere ciddi &#x15F;ekilde sald&#x131;r&#x131;yorlar. Bu y&#xFC;zden de bizler Divine Association olarak Tough Wild Boar'lar&#x131; yok etmeye karar verdik. Sana bu g&#xF6;revi veriyorum. Ruhlar senin yan&#x131;nda, &#x15F;imdi Divine Association ad&#x131;na Tough Wild Boar'lar&#x131; yok et. 
runDlg=T&#xFC;m yarat&#x131;klarla uyum i&#xE7;inde ya&#x15F;ayabilmek i&#xE7;in bunun yap&#x131;lmas&#x131; gerekiyor.
finishDlg=&#x130;&#x15F;i bitirmene sevindim. Bu kadar &#x15F;iddet g&#xF6;stermelerinin bir nedeni varm&#x131;&#x15F;. Divine Association bu nedeni ara&#x15F;t&#x131;racak. &#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Eliminating Tough Wild Boar 
desc=Next mission is eliminating Tough Wild Boar. As a result of my investigation, I knew, it's too late to change them into good stuff. More serious thing is what  they attack villagers. So we Divine Association decided to eliminate Tough Wild Boar. I give you this mission. With Spirits' blessing and the name of Divine Association, eliminate the Tough Wild Boars. 
runDlg=Nothing can be done now for the harmony with other creatures.
finishDlg=I'm pleased you did. There seems to be a reason they get violent. Divine Association will investigate the reason. Good job.
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula008><nsoula009><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Devil Walker'&#x131; Avlama 
desc=Weedridge'in kuzeydo&#x11F;usunda Demon Valley ismi verilen bir yer var. Divine Association'&#x131;n ara&#x15F;t&#x131;rd&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; &#x15F;eytan, s&#xF6;ylenenlere g&#xF6;re burada ya&#x15F;&#x131;yormu&#x15F;. K&#xF6;y&#xFC;n reisi Mark, uzun zamand&#x131;r bu Devil Walker'&#x131; yok etmenin pe&#x15F;inde. Bunu istemesi &#xE7;ok do&#x11F;al &#xE7;&#xFC;nk&#xFC; bu &#x15F;eytan k&#xF6;yl&#xFC;leri rahats&#x131;z ediyor. Biz de bu k&#xF6;ye bir iyilik yapmak ve yard&#x131;m etmek istiyoruz. Demon Valley'e git ve Devil Walker'&#x131; yok et. Bundan sonra ise Mark'a git. 
runDlg=T&#xFC;m Devil Walker'lar&#x131; yok ettin mi? Do&#x11F;ay&#x131; bozmaktan ba&#x15F;ka bir &#x15F;ey yapm&#x131;yorlar. Biz de onlar&#x131;n yok olmalar&#x131;n&#x131; istiyoruz. 
finishDlg=Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler, Cardiff Island &#x15F;imdi yava&#x15F;tan kendine geliyor. Bu y&#xFC;zden de &#xE7;ok mutluyum. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunting Devil Walker 
desc=There is a place named Demon Valley in the northeast of Weedridge. It says that the devil that Divine Association has investigated in these days is living in there. The chief of village, Mark, has longed to eliminate the Devil Walker since long before. It's natural he dislike the devil harassing villagers. So we also plan to help with gratitude in favor of this village. Go to Demon Valley and eliminate Devil Walker. And after that, go to Mark. 
runDlg=Did you eliminate all of Devil Walkers? They are just disrupters of nature we also want to disappear. 
finishDlg=Eliminating what isn't nature is a nice thing in our stance.  Thank to you, Cardiff Island recovers its true self.  So I'm really happy. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula009><nnobi008><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Devil Walker'&#x131;n yok edilmesi 
desc=Weedridge'de huzuru bozanlar&#x131; yok etmenin vakti geldi. Lord, Weedridge'in huzurunu bozan Devil Walker'lara kar&#x15F;&#x131; bir sava&#x15F; ba&#x15F;latt&#x131;. &#x130;&#x15F;te bu y&#xFC;zden biz Noble'lar da Lord'a kat&#x131;laca&#x11F;&#x131;m&#x131;za ve onun isteklerini yerine getirece&#x11F;imize dair s&#xF6;z verdik. Weedridge'in kuzeybat&#x131;s&#x131;nda Demon Valley var. Devil Walker orada ya&#x15F;&#x131;yor. Git ve Devil Walker'lar&#x131; yok et. 
runDlg=L&#xFC;tfen, k&#xF6;ye ve lord'a yard&#x131;m etmelisin. Devil Walker toplulu&#x11F;uyla yap&#x131;lacak sava&#x15F; zor olacakm&#x131;&#x15F; gibi g&#xF6;r&#xFC;n&#xFC;yor, ama &#xF6;yle de&#x11F;il. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Devil Walker'a kar&#x15F;&#x131; ba&#x15F;lat&#x131;lan sava&#x15F;a kat&#x131;lmam&#x131;z konusunda &#x131;srar ediyor. Bir sonraki g&#xF6;revi sana bildirece&#x11F;im.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Elimination of Devil Walker 
desc=It's time to eliminate the disrupters of Weedridge. The lord declared a war against Devil walkers, disrupters of Wedridge. So we nobles gave a firm promise about joining the lord and following lord's will. There is Demon Valley in the northwest of Wedridge. the group of Devil Walker is staying there. Go eliminate Devil Walkers. 
runDlg=&#xB9C8;&#xC744;&#xC744; &#xC704;&#xD574;&#xC11C; &#xC601;&#xC8FC;&#xB2D8;&#xC744; &#xC704;&#xD574;&#xC11C; &#xAF2D; &#xC77C;&#xC744; &#xD574;&#xC8FC;&#xC2DC;&#xAE30; &#xBC14;&#xB78D;&#xB2C8;&#xB2E4;. Devil Walker &#xBB34;&#xB9AC;&#xC640; &#xC804;&#xD22C;&#xB294; &#xC870;&#xAE08; &#xC704;&#xD568;&#xD558;&#xAE34; &#xD558;&#xC9C0;&#xB9CC; &#xADF8;&#xB9AC; &#xC5B4;&#xB824;&#xC6B4; &#xC2F8;&#xC6C0;&#xC740; &#xC544;&#xB2D0;&#xAECD;&#xB2C8;&#xB2E4;. 
finishDlg=Good job. The lord keep on requesting we join the war against Devil Walker. I'll let you know about the next mission. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nnobi008><nwarri008><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Devil Walker Shooter'&#x131;n Yok edilmesi
desc=Lord, mercenary birli&#x11F;inde resmi olarak yard&#x131;m talep etti. G&#xF6;rev, &#x15F;eytan&#x131;n adamlar&#x131;n&#x131; imha etmek. Devil Walker, Cardiff island'da ya&#x15F;&#x131;yor. Epeydir devam eden bu sava&#x15F;, d&#xFC;&#x15F;man&#x131;n m&#xFC;kemmel bir &#x15F;ekilde ortal&#x131;ktan kald&#x131;r&#x131;lmas&#x131;yla son bulmal&#x131;. O halde &#xF6;ncelikle Devil Walker Avc&#x131;lar&#x131;n&#x131; yok edelim. 
runDlg=Bu, &#x15F;eytan&#x131;n adamlar&#x131;na kar&#x15F;&#x131; ba&#x15F;lat&#x131;lan bir sava&#x15F;. Yeteneklerini istedi&#x11F;ini gibi g&#xF6;ster. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Lord bu &#xF6;d&#xFC;l&#xFC; onun yerine sana vermemi istedi. Al bakal&#x131;m. Gelecekte bize daha da &#xE7;ok g&#xF6;rev verecektir. O zaman da bana yard&#x131;m etmeni istiyorum.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Devil Walker Shooter Elimination
desc=The lord legally requested a help to mercenary association. The task is to eliminate devil's men, Devil Walker, living in Cardiff island. This long period of battle should be finish this time with a perfect mop up. Well, at first, let's eliminate Devil Walker Shooters. 
runDlg=Now, This is a battle against devil's men. Show your skill as you like. 
finishDlg=Good job. The lord asked me to give you this reward instead. Here it is. He'll continue to request. I want you to come here again.
</newversion></questtextxml></nwarri008><nwarri009><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=&#x15E;iddetli Devil Walker Shooter'&#x131;n yok edilmesi
desc=Tahmin etti&#x11F;im gibi, Lord bize g&#xF6;revler vermeye devam ediyor. Bu kez bizden &#x15E;iddetli Devil Walker Shooter'lar&#x131; ortadan kald&#x131;rmam&#x131;z&#x131; istiyor. Asl&#x131;nda bu tip g&#xF6;revleri Mercenary Birli&#x11F;i'ne vermesi &#xE7;ok ola&#x11F;an de&#x11F;il. Bizim i&#xE7;in bu tip g&#xF6;revler almak &#xE7;ok iyi, dahas&#x131; bu sayede kendimize olan g&#xFC;venimiz de artar hem. &#x15E;&#x130;mdi git ve bu g&#xF6;revi tamamla. 
runDlg=Daha bitmedi mi? Lord'u bekletmek olmaz. 
finishDlg=Bu i&#x15F;i &#xE7;abucak halletti&#x11F;in i&#xE7;in te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. Lord senin i&#xE7;in bir &#xF6;d&#xFC;l b&#x131;rakt&#x131;. Al bakal&#x131;m, yan&#x131;nda g&#xF6;t&#xFC;r. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Fierce Devil Walker Shooter Elimination
desc=As expected, the lord is requesting continuously. This time he requests the elimination of Fierce Devil Walker Shooters. Well, it's not common he makes these many requests to us, Mercenary Association. It's nice thing for us to receive these requests, and moreover we can also gain confidence. Now, go complete this mission. 
runDlg=Isn't this finished yet? Don't make the lord wait. 
finishDlg=Thanks for your quick handling. The lord gave you a reward. This is your portion. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nwarri009><nwarri010><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Devil Walker Harpooner'&#x131;n Yok edilmesi 
desc=Devil Walker'lar&#x131;n etkisi zay&#x131;fl&#x131;yor ama hala g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC; yarat&#x131;klar mavcut. S&#xF6;zde Devil Walker Harpooner z&#x131;pk&#x131;nlar&#x131;yla insanlara sald&#x131;rd&#x131;. Pek &#xE7;ok k&#xF6;yl&#xFC; bu sald&#x131;r&#x131;dan zarar g&#xF6;rd&#xFC;. Lord bizden, yani Mercenary Birli&#x11F;i'nden onlar&#x131;n yok edilmelerini istedi. Hemen i&#x15F;e koyul. Devil Walker'a kar&#x15F;&#x131; ba&#x15F;latt&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;m&#x131;z sava&#x15F; sona ermek &#xFC;zere. 
runDlg=&#x130;yi gitmiyor mu? E&#x11F;er bu g&#xF6;rev senin becerilerini a&#x15F;&#x131;yorsa etraf&#x131;ndaki meslekta&#x15F;lar&#x131;ndan yard&#x131;m iste. 
finishDlg=Harpooner'lar m&#xFC;kemmel bir &#x15F;ekilde imha edildiler. Lord &#xF6;d&#xFC;l&#xFC;n&#xFC; bana b&#x131;rakt&#x131;. Al bakal&#x131;m. Ah, Jeremiah seni ar&#x131;yor. Ona git. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Devil Walker Harpooner Elimination 
desc=Devil Walkers' influence becomes weak, but there are still some strong creatures. They,  so called Devil Walker Harpooner, attacked people with harpoon. So villagers are suffering from this attack. The lord also requested us, Mercenary Association, their elimination. Eliminate them because the battle against Devil Walker is almost finished. 
runDlg=Isn't it going well?  If it is beyond your ability, ask your colleagues for help around here. 
finishDlg=Harpooners are perfectly eliminated. The lord puts a reward to me. Here it is. Ah, Jeremiah is looking for you. Go to her. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nwarri010><nwarri011><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Mad One-eyed Bat'in G&#xF6;z&#xFC;n&#xFC; Toplama  
desc=Cardiff Abandoned Mine'daki (Cardiff'in Terkedilmi&#x15F; Madeni) yarasalar madencilere sald&#x131;rm&#x131;&#x15F;. Bu y&#xFC;zden art&#x131;k mineral toplamak imkans&#x131;z hale geldi. Di&#x11F;er adalara mineraller ithal ederdik ancak bu yarasalar y&#xFC;z&#xFC;nden Cardiff Island'&#x131;n gelir kayna&#x11F;&#x131; art&#x131;k azal&#x131;yor. Cardiff Island'da ticareti yeniden canlad&#x131;rmak i&#xE7;in Cardiff Abandoned Mine kayna&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; yeniden kullanmaya ba&#x15F;lamal&#x131;y&#x131;z. Git ve Mad One-eyed Bat'i yok et. Yok etti&#x11F;ini g&#xF6;stermek i&#xE7;inse g&#xF6;zlerini getir. 
runDlg=Cardiff Island'da ticaretin yeniden canland&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; g&#xF6;rmek istiyorum. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Bu zorlu bir g&#xF6;revdi, &#xE7;aba g&#xF6;sterdi&#x11F;in i&#xE7;in te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. Sana bir &#xF6;d&#xFC;l verece&#x11F;im. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=The collection of Mad One-eyed Bat's eye  
desc=Bats living in Cardiff Abandoned Mine attacked miners. So it is impossible to collect minerals now. We have exported many minerals to other island, but  owing to bats, Cardiff Island's source of income is decreasing now. For revitalizing Cardiff Island's trade, we must reuse Cardiff Abandoned Mine's resource. Go eliminate Mad One-eyed Bat. Bring bat's eye as a token of elimination. 
runDlg=I'd like to see that fully energetic trade is increasing in Cardiff Island. 
finishDlg=Good job. This was a hard task, but thanks for your effort. I'll give you a reward. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nwarri011><nwarri012><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Carrier Mole Av&#x131;
desc=Madende bir sorun daha var. Carrier Mole'lar&#x131; mallar&#x131; &#xE7;al&#x131;yorlar. S&#xF6;ylenene g&#xF6;re k&#xF6;yl&#xFC;lerin paketlerini alm&#x131;&#x15F;lar ve k&#xF6;yde &#xF6;ylesine dolan&#x131;yorlarm&#x131;&#x15F;. Bir kez daha Cardiff Abandoned Mine'a git ve bu k&#xF6;stebekleri yok et. Bu engelleri ortadan kald&#x131;rmam&#x131;z gerekiyor. 
runDlg=K&#xF6;stebeklerden zarar g&#xF6;ren &#xE7;ok say&#x131;da t&#xFC;ccar var. Daha canl&#x131; ve g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC; bir Cardiff Island i&#xE7;in onlar&#x131; l&#xFC;tfen yok et. 
finishDlg=&#xC7;ok iyi bir i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Cardiff Island '&#x131;n yeniden canland&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; g&#xF6;rebiliyorum.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunting Carrier Mole 
desc=There is another problem in the mine. Carrier Moles are stealing the trade goods. It is said that they have taken villagers' bundles, loitering  around the village. Go one more to Cardiff Abandoned Mine and eliminate these moles. We must be sure to remove these obstacls. 
runDlg=There are many traders that are damaged by the moles. Please eliminate them for a vibrant Cardiff Island. 
finishDlg=You did a good job. We could see a vibrant Cardiff Island again. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nwarri012><nexp010><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Devil Walker Harpooner'&#x131; Yok etme 
desc=Ah, bu g&#xF6;rev senin becerilerini s&#x131;nayacak. Devil Walker gruplar&#x131;n&#x131;n alt&#x131;nda Devil Walker Harpooner'lar var. Yetenekleri m&#xFC;thi&#x15F;tir, &#xE7;abucak geri &#xE7;ekilmeyi ve &#xE7;ok isabetli vurmay&#x131; ba&#x15F;ar&#x131;rlar. Bence, e&#x11F;er senin gibi bir Explorer, bunun gibi bir d&#xFC;&#x15F;manla kar&#x15F;&#x131;la&#x15F;maya haz&#x131;rsa, bununla ayn&#x131; seviyedeki bir d&#xFC;&#x15F;manla nas&#x131;l sava&#x15F;&#x131;laca&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; da &#xF6;&#x11F;renmeli. Devil Walker Harpooner'lar&#x131; yok et. Seni zorlayacaklard&#x131;r, ama siz explorer'lar&#x131;n da harika yetenekleriniz var.
runDlg=D&#xFC;&#x15F;manlar zorlu ama sen de gitgide daha iyi olacaks&#x131;n. Bu tip sava&#x15F;larda ger&#xE7;ek becerilerini g&#xF6;stermen &#xF6;nemli. Elinden gelenin en iyisini yap.
finishDlg=Sonunda -tam da bekledi&#x11F;im gibi- kazanmay&#x131; ba&#x15F;ard&#x131;n. Her &#x15F;eyi ad&#x131;m ad&#x131;m &#xF6;&#x11F;renmek ve &#xF6;&#x11F;rendiklerini sava&#x15F; yeteneklerini geli&#x15F;tirmek ad&#x131;na ger&#xE7;ek sava&#x15F;larda kullanmak &#xF6;nemlidir. Bu tecr&#xFC;beyi akl&#x131;nda tut. &#x130;leride buna benzer bir sava&#x15F;ta yer al&#x131;rsan, bu tecr&#xFC;benin sana &#xE7;ok yard&#x131;m&#x131; dokunacakt&#x131;r. Mark seni ar&#x131;yor. Hemen ona git. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Eliminating Devil Walker Harpooner 
desc=Ah, this mission is for testing your ability. There are Devil Walker Harpooners in a group of Devil Walker. They have a great skill, capable of avoiding quickly and hit correctly. You are an Explorer, and then, I think, you have to learn how to fight against a similar level of enemy. Eliminate Devil Walker Harpooners. They'll be formidable to you, but show you explorers are more excellent .
runDlg=Formidable enemies but you'll be more excellent. Most important thing is your real ability in these kinds of fight. Do your best.
finishDlg=At last you won as I expected. It's important to learn one by one and use in actual fight, if you want to master battle skills. Keep this experience in your mind. When going through a similar battle later, this will be a great help to you. Mark looks for you. Go to him at once. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nexp010><nexp011><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Strong Devil Walker'&#x131;n Kalbini Toplam
desc=Hemen geldi&#x11F;in i&#xE7;in te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. Acil bir &#x15F;ey &#xE7;&#x131;kt&#x131;. Pek &#xE7;ok k&#xF6;yl&#xFC; Devil Walker'a kar&#x15F;&#x131; sava&#x15F;t&#x131;. Sen ve Mercenary Birli&#x11F;i'nin kahramanlar&#x131; sayesinde Devil Walker grubunu kolayl&#x131;kla yok edebildik. Ama bu kez hi&#xE7; umulmad&#x131;k bir &#x15F;ekilde kar&#x15F;&#x131; sald&#x131;r&#x131;da bulundular. Ve Devil Walker'lar aras&#x131;nda &#xE7;ok daha g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC; bir grup var. Biz de haz&#x131;rl&#x131;ks&#x131;z yakaland&#x131;k ve kolayl&#x131;kla yenildik. Strong Devil Walker'lara git ve onlar&#x131; yok et. Onlar&#x131;n g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC; kalplerini onlar&#x131; yok etmenin bir g&#xF6;stergesi olarak buraya getir.
runDlg=G&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC; olmak bir &#x15F;ey de&#x11F;il. Onlar&#x131; keskin ni&#x15F;anc&#x131;l&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;nla alt et.
finishDlg=Evet, bunlar kesinlikle onlar&#x131;n kalpleri. Tamam, kahramanl&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;na kar&#x15F;&#x131;l&#x131;k sana bir &#xF6;d&#xFC;l verece&#x11F;im. Ah, gitmeden &#xF6;nce Jeremiah'ya u&#x11F;ra. Seni ar&#x131;yordu. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collecting Strong Devil Walker's Hear
desc=Thank you for your quick arrival. Something urgent came up. Several villagers fighted against Devil Walker. Thanks to your and Mercenary Association's exploits, we could easily eliminate the group of Devil Walker. But they counterattacked unexpectedly this time. And there is a more strong group among Devil Walkers. So we were off guard and defeated easily. Go to Strong Devil Walkers and eliminate them. Bring the strong heart as a token of elimination.
runDlg=Being strong is not all. Eliminate them with your marksmanship.
finishDlg=Indeed, these are their hearts. OK, I'll give you a reward as your exploits. Ah, go to Jeremia, before you leave. She is looking for you. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nexp011><nexp012><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Stolen Trade Good'lar&#x131; Toplama 
desc=Hemen geldi&#x11F;in i&#xE7;in te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. Cardiff Abandoned Mine'daki ticari mallar&#x131;n ula&#x15F;&#x131;m&#x131; sa&#x11F;lan&#x131;rken pek &#xE7;ok h&#x131;rs&#x131;zl&#x131;k olay&#x131; meydana gelmekte. G&#xF6;r&#xFC;nen o ki, Carrier Mole'lar&#x131; bu mallar&#x131; &#xE7;al&#x131;yor. Bu mallar&#x131; &#xFC;retmektense &#xE7;almak daha &#xE7;ok i&#x15F;lerine geliyor tabii. Git ve Carrier Mole'lar&#x131; yok et ve bana paketlerini getir. Tahminimce bu paketlerden &#xE7;ald&#x131;klar&#x131; ticari mallar &#xE7;&#x131;kacakt&#x131;r. 
runDlg=S&#xF6;ylentiye g&#xF6;re sadece mallar&#x131; &#xE7;almakla kalm&#x131;yor, insanlara da sald&#x131;r&#x131;yorlarm&#x131;&#x15F;. Dikkatli ol! 
finishDlg=Ne muhte&#x15F;em bir &#xE7;aba! Paketlerden tahmin edildi&#x11F;i &#xFC;zere &#xE7;al&#x131;nt&#x131; mallar &#xE7;&#x131;kt&#x131;. &#x130;leride mallar&#x131; ta&#x15F;&#x131;yaca&#x11F;&#x131;m&#x131;z zaman bu k&#xF6;stebeklere kar&#x15F;&#x131; g&#xFC;venli&#x11F;i de iyice art&#x131;r&#x131;r&#x131;z. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collecting Stolen trade goods 
desc=Thank you for quick arrival. During transporting trade goods in Cardiff Abandoned Mine, the cases of burglary are frequently happening. Perhaps Carrier Moles seem to steal trade goods. Because stealing is easier than making themselves. Go eliminate Carrier Moles and bring their bundles. I guess that there are stolen trade goods in the bundles. 
runDlg=There is a rumor that they even attack people as well as stealing trade goods. Be careful! 
finishDlg=You made a great effort. There were all stolen trade goods, as anticipated. In the future when transporting trade goods, we'll takeguar safety measures about guard of these moles. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nexp012><nsoula010><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Essence of the Devil Collection (&#x15E;eytan&#x131;n &#xD6;z&#xFC;n&#xFC; Toplama)
desc=Art&#x131;k Devil Walker'lar&#x131; yok etmenin yan&#x131; s&#x131;ra bir g&#xF6;rev daha var. Bu g&#xF6;rev, Devil Walker'dan Essence of Devil (&#x15E;eytan&#x131;n &#xD6;z&#xFC;n&#xFC;) toplamak. Bu sayede neden Cardiff Island'da kald&#x131;klar&#x131;n&#x131; &#xF6;&#x11F;renece&#x11F;imizi d&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;n&#xFC;yoruz. G&#xF6;r&#xFC;nen t&#xFC;m Devil Walker'lar&#x131; yok et ve &#xF6;zlerini bana getir. 
runDlg=Bu &#xF6;zden &#xE7;ok getirdin mi? En iyisi ruhlar&#x131;n bu konuda s&#xF6;yleyeceklerine kulak vereyim. 
finishDlg=&#xC7;ok &#xF6;z getirmi&#x15F;sin. Ger&#xE7;ekten en iyisini yapt&#x131;n. Bu bilgiyi Divine Association'a ula&#x15F;t&#x131;ray&#x131;m. Ruhlar&#x131;n neler s&#xF6;yleyece&#x11F;ini merak ediyorum. Bay Mark seni &#xE7;a&#x11F;&#x131;r&#x131;yor. G&#xF6;r&#xFC;n&#xFC;&#x15F;e bak&#x131;l&#x131;rsa acilen halledilmesi gereken bir i&#x15F; var. Ona gitsen iyi olacak. .
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=The essence of the devil Collection 
desc=Now you should do one more mission besides eliminating Devil Walkers. That is to collect the essence of devil from Devil Walker. We plan to confirm why they are staying in Cardiff Island. Go eliminate all the visible Devil Walkers. And bring their essence from them. 
runDlg=Did you bring lots of essence? I'd better listen to stories about them from spirits. 
finishDlg=You brought lots of essence. You really did best. I'll deliver this information to Divine Association. I wonder what spirits say. Mr. Mark is calling you. He looks like having some urgent bussiness. You'll be better to go to him. .
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula010><nsoula011><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Fierce Devil Walker Shooter'&#x131;n Yok edilmesi
desc=Oh, sen Jaime'nin g&#xFC;venini kazanan ki&#x15F;i misin? Seni acil bir i&#x15F; i&#xE7;in &#xE7;a&#x11F;&#x131;rd&#x131;m. Devil Walker'a kar&#x15F;&#x131; sava&#x15F; a&#xE7;t&#x131;k &#xE7;&#xFC;nk&#xFC; buran&#x131;n atmosferi iyice k&#xF6;t&#xFC;le&#x15F;ti. K&#xF6;yl&#xFC;leri rahats&#x131;z eden bu &#x15F;eyin yok edilemesini uzun zamand&#x131;r istiyordum ve art&#x131;k sen ve ba&#x15F;ka uzmanlar da Devil Walker'&#x131;n yok edilmesine yard&#x131;mc&#x131; oluyorsunuz. Pek &#xE7;ok g&#xFC;&#xE7;, s&#xFC;rpriz bir sald&#x131;r&#x131;ya haz&#x131;rlan&#x131;yor ama kim bizim uzmanlar&#x131;m&#x131;za kar&#x15F;&#x131; galip gelebilir ki? Git ve Fierce Devil Walker Shooter'lar&#x131; yok et.
runDlg=Daha bitirmedin mi? Acele etme. &#xC7;ok zor bir g&#xF6;rev de&#x11F;il. 
finishDlg=&#xC7;ok iyi. Elbette kimse bizim yetenekli adamlar&#x131;m&#x131;zla boy &#xF6;l&#xE7;&#xFC;&#x15F;emez. Ah, bir iste&#x11F;im var. L&#xFC;tfen biraz bekle. Bu biraz zorlu bir g&#xF6;rev. E&#x11F;er karar&#x131;n&#x131; verdiysen bana s&#xF6;yle. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Fierce Devil Walker Shooter Elimination
desc=Oh, Are you the person who wins Jaime's confidence? I called you for an urgent thing. We declared a war against Devil Walker, as you know the atmosphere. I am very pleasant in thought that eliminates the disrupters of village long before, and you and several experts joined us for eliminating Devil Walker. Several fierce stuff seems to prepare a surprising attack. Well, but, who wins our experts?  Go eliminate Fierce Devil Walker Shooters.
runDlg=Not yet? Take you time. It's not a hard job. 
finishDlg=Good. Indeed no one can be a match for our talented men. Ah, I have a request. Please wait just a while. This is a hard task a little. If you make up your mind, say to me. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula011><nsoula012><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Devil Walker Harpooner'&#x131;n Z&#x131;pk&#x131;n&#x131;n&#x131; Ele ge&#xE7;irme 
desc=Haz&#x131;r m&#x131;s&#x131;n? Bu g&#xF6;rev biraz zor. Bana Devil Walker Harpooner'&#x131;n silah&#x131;n&#x131; getirmen gerekiyor. Elbette, kendimiz de silah yapabiliyoruz ama bence onlar&#x131;n var olmas&#x131;n&#x131; sa&#x11F;layan bu silahlar&#x131; ellerinden almak daha iyi olacak. Devil Walker Harpooner'lar&#x131; yok ettikten sonra silahlar&#x131;n&#x131; topla. 
runDlg=Gel, bir dolu silah al. Sen de bilirsin, ne kadar &#xE7;ok o kadar iyi.
finishDlg=&#xC7;ok iyi. Ah, &#xE7;abalar&#x131;n&#x131;n kar&#x15F;&#x131;l&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; olarak sana bir &#xF6;d&#xFC;l verece&#x11F;im. Bu arada Jaime seni ar&#x131;yor. Do&#x11F;rudan ona git. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Devil Walker Harpooner's Harpooner Collection 
desc=Are you ready? This mission is a little too hard. You have to bring Devil Walker Harpooner's weapon. Of course we also make weapons ourselves, but taking  their existing weapons is much better, I think. Collect Devil Walker Harpooners' weapons after eliminating them. 
runDlg=Bring more weapons. You know more is better.
finishDlg=Good. Ah, I'll give you a reward for your effort. And Jaime is looking for you. Go to her ahead. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula012><nsoula013><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Mad One-eyed Bat'in Kanatlar&#x131;n&#x131; toplama
desc=Sen Mark ile Devil Walker'lar&#x131; temizlerken ben de Cardiff Abandoned Mine'da ba&#x15F; g&#xF6;steren sorunlar&#x131; ara&#x15F;t&#x131;rmaya ba&#x15F;lad&#x131;m. Bu terkedilmi&#x15F; zindana giden insanlar tek g&#xF6;zl&#xFC; yarasalar g&#xF6;rd&#xFC;klerini anlat&#x131;yorlar. Bu yarasalar normal de&#x11F;il. Git ve bu yarasalar&#x131;n kanatlar&#x131;n&#x131; topla. Nas&#x131;l mutantlar olduklar&#x131;n&#x131; ara&#x15F;t&#x131;raca&#x11F;&#x131;m. 
runDlg=Cardiff Island'&#x131;n s&#x131;rlar&#x131; ara&#x15F;t&#x131;rmalar sonunda teker teker a&#xE7;&#x131;&#x11F;a &#xE7;&#x131;kmaya ba&#x15F;l&#x131;yor. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Bana getirece&#x11F;in bilgileri toplamaya devam edece&#x11F;im. Jeremiah senden yard&#x131;m istiyor. L&#xFC;tfen ona git ve yard&#x131;m elini uzat. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collection of Mad One-eyed Bat's wings
desc=While you swept Devil Walkers with Mark, I began to investigate the problems that happened in Cardiff Abandoned Mine. The people who went the abandoned mine said that they had seen one eyed bats. The bats will be not a nomal bat. Go collect the bats' wings. I'll confirm what kind of mutant they are. 
runDlg=The secret of Cardiff Island is getting out one by one, as I investigate. 
finishDlg=Good job. I'll continue to collect the informations you brought.  Jeremiah asks you for help. I hope you go to her and give some help. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula013><nsoula014><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Stolen Trade Good'lar&#x131;n (&#xC7;al&#x131;nan Ticari Mallar) Toplanmas&#x131;
desc=Sen Jamie'nin yollad&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; yeni habercisin. Senin kahramanl&#x131;klar&#x131;n&#x131; uzun s&#xFC;redir duyuyorum. Bu y&#xFC;zden bir iste&#x11F;im olacak. Cardiff Island'&#x131;n ticari mallar&#x131;n&#x131; ta&#x15F;&#x131;rken bir sorun meydana geldi. Cardiff Abandoned Mine'da ya&#x15F;ayan Carrier Mole'lar&#x131;n&#x131;n ticari mallar&#x131; &#xE7;ald&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; duydum. &#xC7;al&#x131;nan bu mallar&#x131; geri getirmeni istiyorum. Cardiff Island'da ticareti yeniden canland&#x131;rmak i&#xE7;in senin yard&#x131;m&#x131;n kesinlikle gerekli. 
runDlg=&#xC7;al&#x131;nan ticari mallar&#x131; geri al. 
finishDlg=&#xC7;ok &#xE7;aba g&#xF6;sterdin. &#xC7;al&#x131;nan mallar&#x131; geri getirdi&#x11F;in i&#xE7;in te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collection of stolen trade goods 
desc=You're the new summoner Jamie sent.I heard your exploits for a long time. So I made a request. A problem occurred while transporting Cardiff Island's trade goods. I heard Carrier Moles who live in Cardiff Abandoned Mine frequently stole trade goods. I want you to get the stolen good back. Your help is surely necessary for active trade of Cardiff Island. 
runDlg=Take the stolen trade goods again. 
finishDlg=You've got a great effort. Thank you for the recovery of the stolen goods.
</newversion></questtextxml></nsoula014><nnobi009><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Devil Walker Shooter'&#x131;n Silah&#x131;n&#x131;n ele ge&#xE7;irilmesi 
desc=G&#xF6;rev, Devil Walker'lar&#x131; silahlar&#x131;ndan mahrum b&#x131;rakmak. Onlar da silah kullan&#x131;yorlar ama biz bu silahlar&#x131; al&#x131;rsak, potansiyelleri azal&#x131;r, &#xF6;yle de&#x11F;il mi? Lorde senden silahlar&#x131; alman&#x131; istiyor. Lord ayr&#x131;ca demirci Mark'a e&#x11F;er bu silahlar&#x131; getirirsen onlar&#x131; eritmesini ve d&#xFC;zeltmesini s&#xF6;yledi. Silahlar&#x131;n&#x131; al ve Mark'a g&#xF6;t&#xFC;r. Onlar&#x131; eritip faydal&#x131; silahlara d&#xF6;n&#xFC;&#x15F;t&#xFC;recek.
runDlg=Toplayabildi&#x11F;in kadar &#xE7;ok silah toplaman daha iyi. B&#xF6;ylece Mark bunlardan daha &#xE7;ok ve de&#x11F;i&#x15F;ik silahlar yapabilir. 
finishDlg=Oh, Devil Walkers'lar&#x131;n silahlar&#x131;. Lord'dan duymu&#x15F;tum. Ama i&#xE7;imden hi&#xE7; bu i&#x15F;le u&#x11F;ra&#x15F;mak gelmiyor &#xE7;&#xFC;nk&#xFC; o silahlar &#x15F;eytanlar taraf&#x131;ndan kullan&#x131;ld&#x131;. &#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Yine Roderick'e git. Hala seni ar&#x131;yor olmal&#x131;. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collection of Devil Walker Shooter's weapon 
desc=This mission is to deprive Devil Walkers of their weapons. They also use weapons, but if we take their weapons, their potential weaken, right? The lord wants  you to take the weapons. The lord also said to blacksmith Mark that if you bring them, make him smelt the weapons inversely. Take their weapons and give them to Mark. He'll smelt them into useful weapons. 
runDlg=It's better you collect as many weapons as possible. Then Mark can make more weapons. 
finishDlg=Oh, Devil Walkers' weapons. I heard about it from the lord. But I don't feel like making them, because of those weapons that devils have been using. Good job. To go to Roderic one more time. Perhaps he will continue to look for you. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nnobi009><nnobi010><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Strong Devil Walker'&#x131;n Yok edilmesi 
desc=Sen ve k&#xF6;yl&#xFC;ler Devil Walker toplulu&#x11F;una sald&#x131;r&#x131;r sald&#x131;rmaz, bu Devil Walker toplulu&#x11F;unda yer alan daha g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC; &#x15F;eytanlar kar&#x15F;&#x131; sald&#x131;r&#x131;ya ge&#xE7;meye &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;t&#x131;lar. Neyse ki &#xE7;ok ciddi bir zarar yok ama y&#xFC;ce lord &#xE7;ileden &#xE7;&#x131;kt&#x131; ve bir daha asla b&#xF6;yle k&#xF6;t&#xFC; varl&#x131;klar&#x131;n ya&#x15F;amas&#x131;na izin vermeyece&#x11F;ini s&#xF6;yledi. Benden onlar&#x131; yok edecek bir uzman bulmam&#x131; istedi. Sen kesinlikle bu i&#x15F; i&#xE7;in do&#x11F;ru adams&#x131;n. Yeniden harekete ge&#xE7;mek kolay. L&#xFC;tfen o aptal Strong Devil Walker'lar&#x131; yok et. Onlara kar&#x15F;&#x131; gelebilecek kadar g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC;s&#xFC;n. 
runDlg=D&#xFC;&#x15F;man kadar g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC;s&#xFC;n, hatta daha da iyisin. Yine de dikkatli ol. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Bunlar &#xF6;nemsiz yarat&#x131;klar. Lord seni ar&#x131;yor. Bu kez ona git. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=The elimination of Strong Devil Walker 
desc=As soon as you and villagers hit the group of Devil Walker, stronger devils in the group of Devil Walkerd tried to counterattack. Fortunately, there wasn't serious damage but the great lord is enraged, saying that he would naver allow such devils. And he asked me for looking for an expert to eliminate them.  Indeed you are the right man. It's easy to preform. Please, eliminate those stupid Strong Devil Walkers. You could stand against them enough. 
runDlg=You could stand against enough, but be careful. 
finishDlg=Good gob. They are trivial creatures. The lord looks for you. Go to him one time. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nnobi010><nnobi011><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Fierce Devil Walker Shooter'&#x131;n Yok edilmesi 
desc=Ah, Roderick'ten senin hakk&#x131;nda bir &#x15F;eyler duyuyorum. Ba&#x15F;latt&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;m bu sava&#x15F;a muhte&#x15F;em bir katk&#x131;da bulunuyorsun. Bu y&#xFC;zden sana bir g&#xF6;rev daha verece&#x11F;im. Devil Walker'lar&#x131;n say&#x131;lar&#x131; s&#xFC;rekli azal&#x131;yor, i&#x15F;te bu y&#xFC;zden pek &#xE7;ok yarat&#x131;k i&#xE7;in hi&#xE7;bir &#x15F;eyin anlam&#x131; kalmad&#x131;, bu da deli k&#xF6;pekler gibi etrafa sald&#x131;rmalar&#x131;na sebep oluyor. Duydu&#x11F;um kadar&#x131;yla son derece h&#x131;zl&#x131; ve de deneyimlilermi&#x15F;. Elbette seninle boy &#xF6;l&#xE7;&#xFC;&#x15F;emezler. Git ve Fierce Devil Walker Shooter'lar&#x131; yok et. Ac&#x131;n&#x131;n tad&#x131;na vars&#x131;nlar bakal&#x131;m. 
runDlg=Hepsini yok etti&#x11F;inden emin ol. Bize bir daha zarar vermelerine izin verme. 
finishDlg=Ha ha ha. &#xC7;ok &#xFC;zg&#xFC;nd&#xFC;m. Bu huzur bozanlar y&#xFC;z&#xFC;nden do&#x11F;ru d&#xFC;zg&#xFC;n d&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;nemiyordum. Senin sayende art&#x131;k sakinle&#x15F;ebilirim.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=The elimination of Fierce Devil Walker Shooter 
desc=Ah, I frequently heard about you from Roderic. You make a significant contribution in the war I declared. So I should have an another request to you. The number of Devil Walkers is continuously decreasing, so several creatures lost their reason and are attacking like a mad dog. But they are faster and very experienced, I heard. Of course, they couldn't be a match for you. go eliminate Fierce Devil Walker Shooters. Let them taste the bitterness. 
runDlg=Sure to eliminate. Never let them damage to us again. 
finishDlg=Ha ha ha, it's very gratifying not to  see the disrupters.
</newversion></questtextxml></nnobi011><nnobi012><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Devil Walker Harpooner'&#x131;n Yok edilmesi 
desc=Bu kadar zor bir i&#x15F;e g&#xF6;re elinden gelenin en iyisini yapt&#x131;n. Ancak bu Devil Walker'lara kar&#x15F;&#x131; ba&#x15F;latt&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;m&#x131;z sava&#x15F; sona ermedi. Pek &#xE7;ok Devil Walker &#xF6;ld&#xFC;kten sonra, kal&#x131;nt&#x131;lar&#x131; ormana gitti ve &#x15F;imdi z&#x131;pk&#x131;nlar atarak oradan ge&#xE7;enlere zarar veriyorlar. Bu bir gerilla sava&#x15F;&#x131;na d&#xF6;nd&#xFC;. Birazc&#x131;k kafalar&#x131; &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;&#x131;yor. Senin g&#xF6;revin o Devil Walker Harpooner'lar&#x131; yok etmek. &#x130;yice bir d&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;n&#xFC;rsen kal&#x131;nt&#x131;lar&#x131; silip s&#xFC;p&#xFC;rmek gerekti&#x11F;ininde fark&#x131;na var&#x131;rs&#x131;n. 
runDlg=Elbette, kal&#x131;nt&#x131;lar&#x131; temizlemek sorunlu bir i&#x15F; ama t&#xFC;m noble'lar&#x131; memnun etmek ad&#x131;na elinden geleni yapaca&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; umuyoruz. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Bu tip &#xF6;nemsiz i&#x15F;lerin geldi&#x11F;i gibi halledilmesi gerekiyor.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=The elimination of Devil Walker Harpooner 
desc=You did best for a difficult job. Yet this war against Devil Walker&#xC640;is not over. After a lot of Devil Walker had died, the remnants of them went in the forest, and now, are harming passersby as throwing harpooners. It's kind of guerilla war. They seem clever a little. Your job is eliminating those Devil Walker Harpooners. Well, think of sweeping the remnants like a spotless room. 
runDlg=Of course, the sweeping of the remnants is troublesome work, but for us nobles, we hope you do better than our thought. 
finishDlg=Good job. These trivial problems should be solved whenever it happens.
</newversion></questtextxml></nnobi012><nnobi013><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Mad One-eyed Bat Av&#x131;
desc=Bundan birka&#xE7; g&#xFC;n &#xF6;nce Cardiff Abandoned Mine'da meydana gelen baz&#x131; olaylardan bahsedeyim sana. Cardiff Abandoned Mine'&#x131;n yan&#x131;ndan ge&#xE7;en bir k&#xF6;yl&#xFC;, bir yarasan&#x131;n sald&#x131;r&#x131;s&#x131;na u&#x11F;ram&#x131;&#x15F;. K&#xF6;yl&#xFC; hayat&#x131;n&#x131; zar zor kurtarm&#x131;&#x15F;, ama yarasan&#x131;n &#xE7;irkin bak&#x131;&#x15F;&#x131;ndan &#xF6;d&#xFC; patlam&#x131;&#x15F;. Bu k&#xF6;yl&#xFC;ye g&#xF6;re yarasan&#x131;n tek bir g&#xF6;z&#xFC; varm&#x131;&#x15F;.  Bu yarat&#x131;k bir mutant. L&#xFC;tfen o yarasalar&#x131; yok et. Bu konu beni gittik&#xE7;e daha da rahats&#x131;z ediyor.
runDlg=Bunlar &#xF6;nemsiz yarat&#x131;klar. Haydi onlar&#x131; iyi bir y&#xFC;rekle temizleyelim. 
finishDlg=&#xC7;abalar&#x131;n i&#xE7;in te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. Ah, Jeremiah seni ar&#x131;yor. Sana sormak istedi&#x11F;i bir &#x15F;ey var gibi.  Jeremiah'y&#x131; ziyaret et. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunting of Mad One-eyed Bat 
desc=Let me tell you about some incident happened in Cardiff Abandoned Mine a few days ago. A villager, who was passing by Cardiff Abandoned Mine, was attacked by a bat. The villager barely saves his life but he's had quite a scare at bat's hideous look. According to the villager, it is said the bat's eye was only one. The creature is a mutant. Please eliminate these bats. That's such a headache more and more. 
runDlg=They are trivial things. Let's sweep with a light heart. 
finishDlg=Thank you for your effort. Ah, Jeremiah is looking for you. There seems something to ask. Go to Jeremiah one time. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nnobi013><nnobi014><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Stolen Trade Good'lar&#x131;n (&#xC7;al&#x131;nan Ticari Mallar) Ele ge&#xE7;irilmesi 
desc=Senin yeteneklerini Lord'dan duydum. Bug&#xFC;nlerde Cardiff Abandoned Mine'da ticari mallar&#x131;n nakliyesi s&#x131;ras&#x131;nda h&#x131;rs&#x131;zl&#x131;k olaylar&#x131; ya&#x15F;an&#x131;yor s&#x131;k s&#x131;k. Ald&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;m&#x131;z bilgiye g&#xF6;re bu mallar&#x131; Carrier Mole'lar &#xE7;al&#x131;yormu&#x15F;. Git ve Carrier Mole'lar&#x131; yok et ve bana paketlerini getir. Belki de &#xE7;al&#x131;nan mallar o paketlerden &#xE7;&#x131;kar. 
runDlg=Lord ayr&#x131;ca Cardiff Island'da ticaretin yeniden canlanmas&#x131;n&#x131; istiyor. Umar&#x131;m sorunu &#xE7;abucak &#xE7;&#xF6;zebildin. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Beklentilerimi kar&#x15F;&#x131;l&#x131;yorsun. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collection for stolen trade goods 
desc=I heard about your ability from the lord. In these days during transporting trade goods, robbery cases are frequently ocurring in Cardiff Abandoned Mine. We get an information Carrier Moles are stealing those trade goods. Go eliminate Carrier Moles and bring the bundles. Perhaps there will be stolen goods in the bundles. 
runDlg=The lord will also want Cardiff Island's trade to become active. I hope you solve the problem in a hurry. 
finishDlg=Good job. You live up to my expectation. 
</newversion></questtextxml></nnobi014><classw001><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Kent ile g&#xF6;r&#xFC;&#x15F;me
desc=Sen &#xE7;aylak, Mercenary'n&#x131;n pozisyonunu mu istiyorsun? Hay&#x131;r, hen&#xFC;z de&#x11F;il. Castle hall'daki Kent'in g&#xFC;venini kazan&#x131;rsan bu konuyu bir kez daha d&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;nece&#x11F;im. 
runDlg=For your greatest choice&#x2026; (En y&#xFC;ce se&#xE7;imin i&#xE7;in&#x2026;)
finishDlg=Buraya neden gelmi&#x15F;tin? 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Elimination of all appearing enemies 
desc=Do you rookie aim at Mercenary's position? Not yet. If you gain confidence from Kent in Castle hall, I'll think about it once again. 
runDlg=For your greatest choice&#x2026;
finishDlg=What do you come here for again? 
</newversion></questtextxml></classw001><classw002><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Token of GUARDIAN'yu bul
Mission2=The Elimination of All Enemies Appearing (Ortaya &#xE7;&#x131;kan t&#xFC;m d&#xFC;&#x15F;manlar&#x131; yok etme)
desc=Bir 'GUARDIAN'&#x131;n hayat&#x131;'n&#x131; m&#x131; istiyorsun, Mercenary? E&#x11F;er istersen sana 'GUARDIAN'l&#x131;k' yetkisi veririm. GUARDIAN &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; kazanmak i&#xE7;in testimden ge&#xE7;melisin. Bu civarda 'Ron' isimli bir ada var. Ve bu adada d&#xF6;v&#xFC;&#x15F;mek i&#xE7;in iyi bir yer var. E&#x11F;er bu 'GUARDIAN'l&#x131;k token'&#x131;n&#x131; al&#x131;rsan d&#xFC;&#x15F;manlar sana sald&#x131;racak. O d&#xFC;&#x15F;manlar&#x131; GUARDIAN token'&#x131;yla yok et. 
runDlg=Sana iyi &#x15F;anslar. Bu g&#xF6;revi tamamlarsan Mercenary'nin di&#x11F;er &#xFC;nvanlar&#x131; i&#xE7;in gerekliIikleri sana anlataca&#x11F;&#x131;m. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. 'GUARDIAN' &#xFC;nvan&#x131; ta&#x15F;&#x131;mana izin veriyorum.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Token of GUARDIAN'yu bul
Mission2=The elimination of all enemies appearing 
desc=Are you a Mercenary  'GUARDIAN's life'? I'll give you 'GUARDIAN's' qulification if you want. For gaining a title to become GUARDIAN, you should pass my test.  There is an island call 'Ron' nearby. And there is a good place to fight in the island. If you take this token of 'GUARDIAN, enemies will attack you. Eliminate the enemies with this token of GUARDIAN. 
runDlg=Good luck to you. I let you know about Mercenary's another title. 
finishDlg=You have done well. I permit 'GUARDIAN's title.
</newversion></questtextxml></classw002><classw003><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Cony Stone&#x2019;yu bul
Mission2=Cony Stone'un Koruyucusu 
desc=Her &#x15F;eyi &#xF6;nleyen adam. Biz ona 'DEFENDER' (savunmac&#x131;) diyoruz. DEFENDER &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; kazanmak i&#xE7;in bir test mevcut. Magnel Island civar&#x131;nda Cony isimli bir ada var. Ve bu da Cony Stone. E&#x11F;er bu ta&#x15F;&#x131; al&#x131;rsan d&#xFC;&#x15F;manlar b&#xFC;y&#xFC;k ihtimalle sana do&#x11F;ru ko&#x15F;acaklard&#x131;r. Senin g&#xF6;revin Cony stone'u bu d&#xFC;&#x15F;manlardan korumak. Ta&#x15F;&#x131; ba&#x15F;ar&#x131;yla koruyabilirsen bana gel. O zaman sana DEPENDER &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; verece&#x11F;im. 
runDlg=Sana iyi &#x15F;anslar. Bir &#xE7;aylak olmak pek ho&#x15F; de&#x11F;il. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. S&#xF6;ylenenler kadar varm&#x131;&#x15F;s&#x131;n. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Cony Stone&#x2019;yu bul
Mission2=The guard of Cony Stone 
desc=The man who blocks all things. We call him 'DEFENDER. There is a test for gaining DEFENDER's title. There is an island called Cony around Magnel Island. And there is Cony Stone, if you take the stone, maybe enemies will crowd into you. Your mission is to guard Cony stone from the enemies. After guarding successfully, come to me. Then I'll give you DEPENDER's' title. 
runDlg=Good luck to you. Nice to be not like rookie. 
finishDlg=Good job. You are as nice as rumors 
</newversion></questtextxml></classw003><classw004><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Rodrigo ile sohbet
desc=Sen de &#x15F;imdi DEFENDER &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; talep ediyorsun. S&#x131;radaki i&#xE7;in kendin karar ver. Bu macera ba&#x15F;lad&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;nda senin kaderine zaten karar verilmi&#x15F;ti. Glostern'deki Rodrigo'ya geri git. Senin i&#xE7;in b&#xFC;y&#xFC;k ihtimalle son bir testi vard&#x131;r.
finishDlg=Oh, buna inanm&#x131;yorum. Bir &#xE7;aylak bu &#xFC;nvan&#x131; talep edemez! 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conversation with Rodrigo 
desc=You also acquire DEfENDER's 'title now. Decide yourself about the next. Your fate would be already decided when starting this advanture. Go back to Rodrigo in Glostun. He will probably have a final selection to you.
finishDlg=Oh, I don' believe. A rookie acquires this title! 
</newversion></questtextxml></classw004><classe001><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Crow ile sohbet
desc=Kaderine karar vermenin vakti geldi. Castle Hall'daki Crow'a anlataca&#x11F;&#x131;m, bu y&#xFC;zden orada kaderin belirlendikten sonra buraya gel. &#xC7;ok kolay olmayacak &#xE7;&#xFC;nk&#xFC; yol biraz zorludur. 
runDlg=Bu harika bir kader! 
finishDlg=Um, bunu Ruskin'den duydum. Bundan sonra iki kaderin aras&#x131;nda karar vermenin vakti geldi. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=The conversation with Crow 
desc=It's time to decide your fate. I'll tell Crow in the Castle Hall, so come here after deciding your fate there. It'll be not easy because of a rough itinerary. 
runDlg=What a nice fate! 
finishDlg=Um, I heard this from Ruskin. You should decide between your two fate from now. 
</newversion></questtextxml></classe001><classe002><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=11 dakika i&#xE7;inde Patus'u yok etmek 
desc=&#x15E;u an geli&#x15F;tirdikleri y&#xF6;ne bak&#x131;l&#x131;rsa Explorer'lar farkl&#x131; yollara gidiyorlar. Hangi y&#xF6;n&#xFC; istiyorsun bilmiyorum ama sana birini &#xF6;&#x11F;retece&#x11F;im. &#xD6;ncesinde seni test edece&#x11F;im. Ignis, Lava Plateau'daki tehlikeli varl&#x131;k olarak bilinir. Ve bu civarda Patus ismini ta&#x15F;&#x131;yan baz&#x131; yarat&#x131;klar vard&#x131;r. Bunlar Ignis'i takip eden astlar&#x131; gibidirler. Bunlar&#x131; yok etmek &#xE7;ok kolay de&#x11F;ildir &#xE7;&#xFC;nk&#xFC; &#xE7;ok h&#x131;zl&#x131; ve de kurnazca hareket ederler. Ama ben senin daha da h&#x131;zl&#x131; ve hatas&#x131;z olman&#x131; istiyorum. 10 Patus yok ettikten 10 dakika sonra geri gel. Sonra sana  HUNTER &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; sunaca&#x11F;&#x131;m
runDlg=Kolay de&#x11F;ilmi&#x15F;, &#xF6;yle de&#x11F;il mi?  HUNTER'&#x131;n rol&#xFC; bu yetene&#x11F;in kendisi kadar zordur. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Harika! Sana HUNTER &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; veriyorum ancak, bir Explorer'&#x131;n yapaca&#x11F;&#x131; bir &#x15F;ey daha var. O da BLASTER. E&#x11F;er s&#x131;radaki g&#xF6;revi de yerine getirebilirsen BLASTER &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; sunaca&#x11F;&#x131;m sana. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Eliminating Patus within 17 minutes 
desc=According to his developing direction,  Explorers go their own load, not to the same load. I don't know the load you want, but I'll teach you about one load. I'll test you before that. There is Ignis, known as a dangerous existence, in Lava Plateau. And around the place, there are some creatures named Patus. They are underlings who follow Ignis. It is not easy to eliminate them because their movements are quick and shrewd. But want you to show being more quick and correct than the underlings. Come back with 10 minutes after eliminating 10 Patuses. Then I'll confer the title of HUNTER
runDlg=Not easy, right? HUNTER's role is difficult as much as the ability. 
finishDlg=Good job. Wonderful! I gave HUNTER's title, but an Explorer can do one more thing. That's just BLASTER. If you carry out next imssion, I'll confer the title of BLASTER. 
</newversion></questtextxml></classe002><classe003><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Wisp'in &#xC7;ekirde&#x11F;ini Ele ge&#xE7;irme
Mission2=Flame Crewbarian'&#x131;n K&#xFC;rk&#xFC;n&#xFC; Toplama
Mission3=Patus Par&#xE7;alar&#x131;n&#x131; toplama
desc=Blaster'lar genel yerlerdeki gizli &#x15F;eyleri bulurlar. S&#x131;radaki alanda senden istedi&#x11F;im &#x15F;eyi bulursan, sana BLASTER &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; verece&#x11F;im. 
 Wisp of Lava Plateau'dan Wisp'in &#xC7;ekirde&#x11F;i, Flame Crewbarian'dan Flame Crewbarian'&#x131;n K&#xFC;rk&#xFC;, Patus'tan Patus Par&#xE7;alar&#x131;. 
runDlg=Daha bitiremedin mi? Haha, kolay kolay bulabilece&#x11F;in bir &#x15F;ey de&#x11F;il o. 
finishDlg=Harika! Nas&#x131;l bulabildin? S&#xF6;z verdi&#x11F;im gibi, sana Blaster &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; verece&#x11F;im. Glostern'deki Ruskin'e geri d&#xF6;n. Ona bunu iletece&#x11F;im. Yani sadece bu iki unvan aras&#x131;nda se&#xE7;im yapman gerekiyor. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collecting The core of Wisp
Mission2=Collecting Flame Crewbarian's fur
Mission3=Collecting Patus' pieces
desc=Blasters often find mysterious things in the common place. If you fine what I say now in next area, I'll give you BLASTER's title. 
 Wisp's core from Wisp of Lava Plateau, Flame Crewbarian's fur from Flame Crewbarian, Patus' pieces from Patus. 
runDlg=Not yet? Haha, that is not something you find esaily. 
finishDlg=Great! How did you find it? As I promised, I'll give you Blaster's title. Turn back to Ruskin in Glostun. I'll tell him in advance. So you have only  to choose one between the two titles. 
</newversion></questtextxml></classe003><classn001><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Lloyd ile sohbet
desc=G&#xF6;r&#xFC;n&#xFC;&#x15F;e g&#xF6;re buraya b&#xFC;y&#xFC; &#xFC;zerinde ustala&#x15F;maya gelmi&#x15F;sin. Seni biriyle tan&#x131;&#x15F;t&#x131;ray&#x131;m. Ad&#x131; Lloyd ve 'Ron' isimli bir adada bir bar i&#x15F;letiyor. Kendisi b&#xFC;y&#xFC;n&#xFC;n ba&#x15F;ka bir alan&#x131;nda uzmand&#x131;r ve sana kara b&#xFC;y&#xFC;y&#xFC; g&#xF6;sterecek. Seni ayr&#x131;ca beyaz b&#xFC;y&#xFC;y&#xFC; bilen biriyle de tan&#x131;&#x15F;t&#x131;racak. Her ikisinde de uzmanla&#x15F;. Sonras&#x131;nda kaderine karar verece&#x11F;im. 
runDlg=Bunlar sayg&#x131;n iki kader. 
finishDlg=Seni bu k&#xFC;&#xE7;&#xFC;k adaya getiren &#x15F;ey nedir? 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conversation with Lloyd
desc=You seem to come here for mastering magic. I introduce a person to you. His name is Lloyd and runs a bar in an island called 'Ron'. He, who mastered the flipside of magic, will let you know about black magic. And also he introduce a person to you, knowing the magic of directing right path. Master all of the two. Then I'll decide your fate. 
runDlg=This is honorable two fates. 
finishDlg=What's up to this small island? 
</newversion></questtextxml></classn001><classn002><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=The Collection of an Old Magic Book (Eski bir b&#xFC;y&#xFC; kitab&#x131;n&#x131;n ele ge&#xE7;irilmesi)
desc=Ah, farkl&#x131; bir b&#xFC;y&#xFC; konusunda ustala&#x15F;mak i&#xE7;in gelmi&#x15F;sin buraya. Ruhun Noble'&#x131;nkiyle benze&#x15F;miyor. Sana istedi&#x11F;in &#x15F;eyi &#xF6;&#x11F;retmek yerine bir g&#xF6;rev verece&#x11F;im. Magnel Island'daki Lava Plateau'da Strong Volcano Imp'leri mevcut. Bunlar&#x131;n aras&#x131;ndaki baz&#x131; cinlerde ise eski b&#xFC;y&#xFC; kitaplar&#x131; var. L&#xFC;tfen o kitaplar&#x131; bana getir. 
runDlg=Kitaplar sadece baz&#x131; cinlerde oldu&#x11F;undan, &#xE7;ok say&#x131;da cini yok etmelisin. 
finishDlg=Oh! &#x130;&#x15F;te bunlar. Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. Sahip oldu&#x11F;um b&#xFC;y&#xFC; bilgisini seninle payla&#x15F;aca&#x11F;&#x131;m. Sonras&#x131;nda 'SOLEKNIGHT' olma hakk&#x131;n&#x131; kazanabileceksin. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=The collection of an old magic book 
desc=Ah, you come here for mastering the flipside of magic. Your spirit appears to be not the same for Noble's. Instead of teaching what you want, I'll ask you a request. There are Strong Volcano Imps at Lave Plateau of Magnel Island. Several imps among them have the old magic books. Please, bring the books to me. 
runDlg=Because only several imps have the books, you should eliminate a lot of imps. 
finishDlg=Oh! This is the one. Thank you. I'll let you know about the knowledge of magic I have. Then you'll be qualified for becoming 'SOLEKNIGHT'. 
</newversion></questtextxml></classn002><classn003><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Lady Avery ile sohbet 
desc=&#x15E;imdi seni b&#xFC;y&#xFC;n&#xFC;n bir ba&#x15F;ka y&#xF6;n&#xFC;n&#xFC; &#xF6;&#x11F;retecek biriyle tan&#x131;&#x15F;t&#x131;ray&#x131;m. L&#xFC;tfen Exeter Island'da Lady Avery'yi ziyaret et. Sana muhtemelen farkl&#x131; t&#xFC;rde bir b&#xFC;y&#xFC; &#xF6;&#x11F;retecektir. Noble resmi olarak b&#xFC;y&#xFC;y&#xFC; &#xF6;&#x11F;rendi, dolay&#x131;s&#x131;yla o da sana Noble'&#x131;n b&#xFC;y&#xFC;y&#xFC; nas&#x131;l kulland&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; anlatacakt&#x131;r.
finishDlg=Sen&#x2026;benden Noble'&#x131;n b&#xFC;y&#xFC;s&#xFC;n&#xFC; &#xF6;&#x11F;renmek i&#xE7;in geldin. Do&#x11F;ru karar.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conversation with Lady Avery 
desc=&#xB2E4;&#xB978; &#xB9C8;&#xBC95;&#xC758; &#xAE38;&#xC744; &#xC54C;&#xB824;&#xC904; &#xC0AC;&#xB78C;&#xC744; &#xC18C;&#xAC1C;&#xD558;&#xC8E0;. Exeter Island&#xC758;Lady Avery&#xB97C; &#xCC3E;&#xC544;&#xAC00; &#xBCF4;&#xC2DC;&#xAE30; &#xBC14;&#xB78D;&#xB2C8;&#xB2E4;. &#xADF8;&#xB140;&#xAC00; &#xC544;&#xB9C8; &#xB2E4;&#xB978; &#xB9C8;&#xBC95;&#xC744; &#xAE38;&#xC744; &#xC54C;&#xB824;&#xC904; &#xAC83;&#xC785;&#xB2C8;&#xB2E4;. &#xC815;&#xC2DD;&#xC73C;&#xB85C; Noble&#xC758; &#xB9C8;&#xBC95;&#xC744; &#xBC30;&#xC6B4; &#xADF8;&#xB140;&#xB294; &#xC544;&#xB9C8; &#xC815;&#xB3C4;&#xC758; Noble &#xB9C8;&#xBC95;&#xC5D0; &#xB300;&#xD574;&#xC11C; &#xC54C;&#xB824;&#xC904; &#xAC83;&#xC785;&#xB2C8;&#xB2E4;.
finishDlg=&#xB2F9;&#xC2E0;&#xC740;&#x2026;&#xB098;&#xC5D0;&#xAC8C; &#xADC0;&#xC871; &#xB9C8;&#xBC95;&#xC5D0; &#xB300;&#xD574;&#xC11C; &#xBC30;&#xC6B0;&#xB7EC; &#xC654;&#xAD70;. &#xC798; &#xC624;&#xC168;&#xC18C;
</newversion></questtextxml></classn003><classn004><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Recovering Noble's Missing Book (Noble'&#x131;n kay&#x131;p kitab&#x131;n&#x131;n iyile&#x15F;tirilmesi)
desc=Sana &#xF6;&#x11F;reteceklerim sadece do&#x11F;ru yolu izleyen noble'lara verilmi&#x15F;tir. Bunlara 'MAGE' ad&#x131; verilir. Sana elbette 'MAGE &#xFC;nvan&#x131; verebilirim, ama &#xF6;nce bir g&#xF6;revi yerine getirmelisin. Noble Masquer'in uzun zaman &#xF6;nce kaybetti&#x11F;i bir kitap var. Magnel Island'daki Lava Plateau'da kalan Imp Leader'inin bu kitab&#x131; ele ge&#xE7;irdi&#x11F;ine dair bilgiye sahibim. Bu kitab&#x131; getir. Sonras&#x131;nda sana MAGE &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; verece&#x11F;im. 
runDlg=Bana kitab&#x131; getirece&#x11F;ini &#xFC;mit ediyorum. 
finishDlg=Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. Sana MAGE &#xFC;nvan&#x131;n&#x131; verece&#x11F;im. Ian'a geri d&#xF6;n ve kaderine karar ver. &#x130;yi &#x15F;anslar.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Recovering noble's missing book 
desc=What I teach is to be delivered to the nobles who have pursuited only right direction. They are called as 'MAGE'. Of course I could give you 'MAGE's title, but you have to receive a request.  There is a book lost in Noble Masquer a long time ago. I get an information that Imp Leader has the book, staying at Lava Plateau of  Magnel Island.  Bring the book. Then I'll give you MAGE's title. 
runDlg=I wish you would bring the book. 
finishDlg=Thank you. I'll qualify you for MAGE. Go back to Iann and decide you fate. Good luck to you.
</newversion></questtextxml></classn004><classn005><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Ian ile sohbet
desc=Bir maceraya at&#x131;l&#x131;rken burada kazand&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n &#xFC;nvanlardan birini se&#xE7;men gerekecek. Hangisini se&#xE7;ersen se&#xE7;, umar&#x131;m pi&#x15F;man olmazs&#x131;n. 
runDlg=B&#xFC;y&#xFC; yolunu a&#xE7;&#x131;k etsin. 
finishDlg=Tebrikler. Umar&#x131;m gelece&#x11F;inde zaferler olur. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conversation with Ian 
desc=You have to choose one among the titles you gained when having an adventure. Whatever you choose, I hope you are not regrettable. 
runDlg=Magic led you. 
finishDlg=Congratulation. I wish the honor is with you in your future. 
</newversion></questtextxml></classn005><classs001><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Shaman Puck ile sohbet 
desc=Do&#x11F;al olarak kaderine karar verilmi&#x15F; olacak. Gitme vakti. Cardiff Island'daki Shaman Puck'a git. Belki de kaderine karar verecek ki&#x15F;i odur. 
runDlg=Do&#x11F;a ismini f&#x131;s&#x131;ld&#x131;yor. 
finishDlg=Uh? Sen de kimsin?
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conversation with Shaman Puck 
desc=Nature are going to decide you fate. It's time to go. Go to Shaman Puck in Cardiff Island. Perhaps he becomes the man who decide your fate. 
runDlg=Nature is wispering with your name. 
finishDlg=Uh? Who are you?
</newversion></questtextxml></classs001><classs002><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Fox Den'deki Skull Monument'i yok etme  
Mission2=Lava Plateau'daki Patus'u yok etme
Mission3=Castle Field'daki Tiger Spider'&#x131; yok etme
desc=Ah, sen beni kabuslar&#x131;mdan kurtaran ki&#x15F;isin. Ne? Benim gibi bir SHAMAN m&#x131; olmak istiyorsun yoksa? Bu kolay ama &#xF6;nce ruhlarla g&#xF6;r&#xFC;&#x15F;mem gerekiyor. Her &#x15F;eyi yok edebilecek &#xFC;st&#xFC;nl&#xFC;kte bir &#x15F;eye sadece Ruhlar karar verebilir. SHAMAN &#xFC;nvan&#x131; i&#xE7;in &#x15F;u hedefleri yok et. 
  Skull Monument of Fox Den, Patus of Lava Plateau, Tiger Spider of Castle Field. 
runDlg=Do&#x11F;an&#x131;n ve ruhlar&#x131;n g&#xFC;c&#xFC;n&#xFC; birlikte hisset. 
finishDlg=Tebrikler. Bir SHAMAN olarak an&#x131;labilmen i&#xE7;in onay verece&#x11F;im.  &#x15E;imdi Castle Hall'daki Ross'a git. Sana Saint'ten bahsedecek. Ross'a git. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Destroying Skull Munument at Fox Den  
Mission2=Eliminating Patus at Lava Plateau Patus 
Mission3=Eliminating Tiger spider in Castle Field
desc=Ah, You are the man who rescued me from nightmare. What? Are you saying that you'd like to be SHAMAN like me? It's easy but I should converse with spirits in advance. Spirits only can permit the right that destroy anything from nature's power. For SHAMAN's title, eliminate the following stuff. 
  Skull Monument of Fox Den, Patus of Lava Plateau, Tiger Spider of Castle Field. 
runDlg=Feel nature's and sprit's power togethr. 
finishDlg=Congratulation. I'll give the title as a SHAMAN who I also recognized. Go to Ross at Castle Hall, then he'll say to you Saint's another load. Go to Ross. 
</newversion></questtextxml></classs002><classs003><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Ross ile sohbet 
desc=Ho&#x15F;geldin. Buraya iyile&#x15F;tirme yetene&#x11F;ini &#xF6;&#x11F;renmek i&#xE7;in mi geldin? Bu &#xE7;ok zor de&#x11F;il. &#x130;yile&#x15F;tirmek i&#xE7;in Saint'in yetene&#x11F;ini istiyorsan sana &#xF6;zellikle o yetene&#x11F;i &#xF6;&#x11F;retece&#x11F;im. Hasta yarat&#x131;klar&#x131; iyile&#x15F;tirmek de Saint'in g&#xF6;revlerindendir. Sana verdi&#x11F;im g&#xF6;revin alt&#x131;ndan kusursuz bir &#x15F;ekilde kalkarsan seni PRIEST yapaca&#x11F;&#x131;m. 
finishDlg=&#x15E;imdi, g&#xF6;revi yerine getirmeye haz&#x131;r m&#x131;s&#x131;n? 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conservation with Ross 
desc=Welcome. Do you come here for the skill of cure? It's not difficult thing. If you want Saint's skill to cure, I'll teach you the skill especially. Curing ill creatures is also one of Saint's role. If you perfectly perform a mission I want, I'll qualify you for PRIEST. 
finishDlg=Now, are you ready to carry out the mission? 
</newversion></questtextxml></classs003><classs004><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Mark ile sohbet
desc=Roxbury'de &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;an Mark, mide a&#x11F;r&#x131;s&#x131; &#xE7;ekiyor. Etrafta da doktor yok. Mark'a git ve mide a&#x11F;r&#x131;s&#x131;n&#x131; iyile&#x15F;tir. Onu iyile&#x15F;tirdikten sonra buraya geri gel. Burada iyile&#x15F;tirilecek &#xE7;ok hasta var. 
runDlg=Ooh&#x2026;. Uzun zamand&#x131;r g&#xF6;r&#xFC;&#x15F;m&#xFC;yoruz. Buraya bana yard&#x131;m etmek i&#xE7;in mi geldin? 
finishDlg=Oh? A&#x11F;r&#x131; ge&#xE7;ti. Beni iyile&#x15F;tirdin mi? Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;r ederim. B&#xF6;yle bir yetene&#x11F;i ne zaman &#xF6;&#x11F;rendin? Yine de te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Mark&#xC640; &#xB300;&#xD654;
desc=Mark, working eagerly in Roxbury, is surffering from stomach ache. There seems no doctor. Go to Mark and cure his stomach ache. After curing him, come back here. Here are a lot of patients to cure. 
runDlg=Ooh&#x2026;. Long time no see. Do you come here for help me? 
finishDlg=Uh? Pain's disappeared. Did you cure me?  Thank for this. When did you learn such a skill? Thank you anyway. 
</newversion></questtextxml></classs004><classs005><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Lord Lionel ile sohbet 
desc=Bundan sonra da Roxbury'deki Lord Lionel'&#x131; iyile&#x15F;tirmelisin. Bu hi&#xE7; de &#xE7;ekici bir g&#xF6;rev de&#x11F;il ama Roxbury'nin h&#xFC;k&#xFC;mdar&#x131;n&#x131; da g&#xF6;rmezden gelemem. Son zamanlarda ba&#x15F;&#x131; &#xE7;ok fena a&#x11F;r&#x131;yormu&#x15F;. Oraya git ve onu iyile&#x15F;tir. 
runDlg=Uh? Uzun zamandan beri g&#xF6;r&#xFC;&#x15F;m&#xFC;yoruz. Benimle bir i&#x15F;in mi vard&#x131;? 
finishDlg=Huh, ba&#x15F; a&#x11F;r&#x131;m tamamen ge&#xE7;ti. Bu inan&#x131;lmaz. Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conversation with Lord Lionel 
desc=Next you should cure Lord Lionel in Roxbury. This job is a very uninviting thing to do, but I can't just pretend not to know the ruler of Roxbury. He has had headache recently. Go to him and cure. 
runDlg=Uh? Long time no see. Do you have business to me? 
finishDlg=Huh, My headache is clear completely. It's amazing. Thank you. 
</newversion></questtextxml></classs005><classs006><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=General Renfield ile sohbet
desc=&#x15E;imdi iyile&#x15F;tirece&#x11F;imiz ki&#x15F;i ise bu k&#xF6;yde ya&#x15F;ayan General Renfield. Duydu&#x11F;um kadar&#x131;yla aya&#x11F;&#x131;nda mantar varm&#x131;&#x15F;. Hemen iyile&#x15F;tirilse daha iyi olacak. Git ve mantar&#x131; iyile&#x15F;tir. Bunu takdir edecektir.
runDlg=Um, Bu da kim? Benimle nas&#x131;l bir i&#x15F;in var? 
finishDlg=Oh! Aman. Mantar&#x131;m nas&#x131;l oldu da bir anda ge&#xE7;ti? Sana nas&#x131;l te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;r edebilirim? 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=The conversation with General Renfield 
desc=The next cure is General Renfield living in this village. I heard that he is surffering from athlete's foot. Well, chronic desease is better as quickly as possible. Go and treat the athlete's foot. He sure to be pleasant. 
runDlg=Um, Who is this? What business do you have? 
finishDlg=Oh! Dear. How can my athelete's foot heal completely? How can I say thank you? 
</newversion></questtextxml></classs006><classs007><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Lizzie ile sohbet 
desc=Oh, iyi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Sen ruhlar&#x131;n se&#xE7;ti&#x11F;i ki&#x15F;isin, kesinlikle. &#x15E;imdi iyile&#x15F;tirece&#x11F;in Lizzie haz&#x131;ms&#x131;zl&#x131;k &#xE7;ekiyor. Belki de yeni bir yemek yaparken zehirlenmi&#x15F;tir. Lizzie'ye git ve ona yard&#x131;m et.
runDlg=Uh? Neler oluyor? 
finishDlg=Oh, inanm&#x131;yorum! Midem d&#xFC;zeldi. Beni iyile&#x15F;tirdin mi? Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler! 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=The conversation with Lizzie 
desc=Oh, good job. You are the man who spirits chose, indeed. The next is to cure Lizzie who has indigestion. He maybe eat bad food while cooking a new dish. Go to Lizzie and help her.
runDlg=Uh? What up? 
finishDlg=Oh, dear! My stomach is settled. Did you cure me? Thank you! 
</newversion></questtextxml></classs007><classs008><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Lady Avery ile sohbet 
desc=S&#x131;radaki hasta Glostern'deki lord Lady Avery. A&#x11F;&#x131;r i&#x15F;leri y&#xFC;z&#xFC;nden &#xE7;ok uzun s&#xFC;re d&#x131;&#x15F;ar&#x131;da kalm&#x131;&#x15F; olabilir ve bu &#x15F;ekilde ba&#x15F;&#x131;na g&#xFC;ne&#x15F; ge&#xE7;mi&#x15F;tir. Oraya git ve onu iyile&#x15F;tir.  
runDlg=Buraya neden geldin?
finishDlg=Oh, kendime taptaze hissediyorum. Beni iyile&#x15F;tirdin mi? Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conversation with Lady Avery 
desc=Next patient is the lord Lady Avery in Glostern. Because of heavy work, maybe the lord went around outside for a long time and has heatstroke. Go to her and cure.  
runDlg=What brings you here?
finishDlg=Oh, I feel refreshed again. Did you cure me? Thank you. 
</newversion></questtextxml></classs008><classs009><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Roland ile sohbet 
desc=S&#x131;radaki hasta Glostern'deki Roland. Ormandayken bir y&#x131;lan sokmu&#x15F; ve zehirlenmi&#x15F;. Git ve onu iyile&#x15F;tir. Acele et ki zehir t&#xFC;m v&#xFC;cuda yay&#x131;lmas&#x131;n. 
runDlg=Uh, l&#xFC;tfen, bir doktor &#xE7;a&#x11F;&#x131;r&#x131;n! 
finishDlg=Uh, oh&#x2026; g&#xF6;r&#xFC;n&#xFC;&#x15F;e g&#xF6;re zehir v&#xFC;cudumu terk ediyor. Beni iyile&#x15F;tirdin mi? Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler, ho, ho! 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conversation with Roland 
desc=Next patient is Roland living in Glostern. He was poisoned by snake after going in the forest. Go to him and cure. Hurry up as not to spread throughout the whole body. 
runDlg=Oop, please, call a doctor. 
finishDlg=Uh, oh&#x2026; poison looks like leaving my body. Did you cure me? Thank you, ho, ho! 
</newversion></questtextxml></classs009><classs010><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Jonathan ile sohbet 
desc=Vay be, hastalara &#xE7;ok iyi bakt&#x131;n. Bir 'PRIEST' olmak i&#xE7;in tam kapasiteye sahipsin. Bir Saint'in se&#xE7;ebilece&#x11F;i y&#xF6;nlerden birini dikkatlice se&#xE7;, iyi bir se&#xE7;im yap ki sonra pi&#x15F;man olma. Glostern'deki Jonathan'a git. Seni do&#x11F;an&#x131;n y&#xF6;n&#xFC;ne (nature's load) y&#xF6;nlendirecek. 
runDlg=Do&#x11F;a seni kutsas&#x131;n! 
finishDlg=Tebrikler. Do&#x11F;an&#x131;n sesi sana &#xF6;nc&#xFC;l&#xFC;k ediyor. &#x15E;imdi kaderini se&#xE7;. Hangisini se&#xE7;ersen se&#xE7; do&#x11F;a sana do&#x11F;ru yolu g&#xF6;sterecektir. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conversation with Jonathan 
desc=Wow, you carry out a wonderful cure for ill patients. You fully have a capability for 'PRIEST'. Decreetly get one load not to regret, among the loads Saint could choose. Turn back to Jonathan in Glostun. He'll lead you to nature's load. 
runDlg=Nature bless you! 
finishDlg=Congratulation. Nature's voice led you. Choose your fate now. Nature will lead you to a righ load whatever you choose. 
</newversion></questtextxml></classs010><ad3b10001><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=&#x15E;&#xFC;pheli dok&#xFC;manlar&#x131; toplama 
desc=Merhaba, epeydir g&#xF6;r&#xFC;&#x15F;m&#xFC;yoruz. Senden b&#xF6;ylesine b&#xFC;y&#xFC;k bir istekte bulunmak istemezdim, &#xFC;zg&#xFC;n&#xFC;m. Son zamanlarda Fox Den civar&#x131;nda garip bir ma&#x11F;ara bulundu.  Pek &#xE7;ok ka&#x15F;if b&#xFC;y&#xFC;k bir merakla ma&#x11F;araya girdiler ancak hepsi de korkuyla -sanki &#x15F;eytan ruhlar&#x131;n&#x131; ele ge&#xE7;irmi&#x15F; gibi- oradan ka&#xE7;t&#x131;lar. Daha sonralar&#x131; duydum ki, korkun&#xE7; &#x15F;eyler g&#xF6;rm&#xFC;&#x15F;ler, insan olmayan &#x15F;eyler. Umar&#x131;m sen gelebilir ve de bu ma&#x11F;araya bir g&#xF6;z atabilirsin. &#xC7;ok korkun&#xE7; bir &#x15F;ey g&#xF6;rmeye haz&#x131;rla kendini. Werefox'lar&#x131; yok ederken bir &#x15F;eyler bulursan l&#xFC;tfen bu k&#xF6;ye geri d&#xF6;n ve bana olanlar&#x131; bildir. 
runDlg=Bu ma&#x11F;aray&#x131; ke&#x15F;fettikten sonra bu k&#xF6;y&#xFC;n atmosferi de&#x11F;i&#x15F;ti, daha g&#xFC;r&#xFC;lt&#xFC;l&#xFC; ve huzursuz bir yer oldu buras&#x131;. Bu belay&#x131; hemen yok et. 
finishDlg=Vay can&#x131;na, ne kadar tehlikeli olursa olsun, o tehlikeli yerden bir &#x15F;eylerle geldin. &#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. &#x130;ncelemelerden sonra sana s&#x131;radaki g&#xF6;revini verece&#x11F;im. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collecting doubtful documents 
desc=Hi, long time no see. Sorry for this big request before sharing our pleasure. A strange cave was found around Fox Den before long. Several explorers had come into the cave with curiosity, but they all escaped with fear, like being possessed by a devil. Later I heard that they's seen horrible things, but not humen. I hope you come here and look into the cave. Be careful for something horrible. If you find some stuff  while eliminating  Werefoxes, please turn back this village and let me know about it without delay. 
runDlg=After the discovery of the cave, an atmosphere of this village is noisy and uneasy. Get rid of them quickly. 
finishDlg=Oh, you come here with something from the dangerous place. Good job. I'll give you next mission after examination. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10001><ad3b10002><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Werefox's kuyru&#x11F;unu Jaime teslim et
desc=Bu d&#xF6;k&#xFC;mana g&#xF6;re orada bir deney yap&#x131;l&#x131;yormu&#x15F;. &#xC7;ok fazla ayr&#x131;nt&#x131; mevcut de&#x11F;il ancak bu deneyde insan bedenlerinin kullan&#x131;ld&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; a&#xE7;&#x131;k. O deney s&#x131;ras&#x131;nda &#xE7;ok korkun&#xE7; &#x15F;eylerin ya&#x15F;and&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; d&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;n&#xFC;yorum. Jamie'ye s&#xF6;yledim, e&#x11F;er Werefox kuyru&#x11F;u toplar ve getirirsen Jamie onlar&#x131; inceleyecek. 
runDlg=Bu tehlikeli ma&#x11F;arada neler d&#xF6;nd&#xFC;&#x11F;&#xFC;n&#xFC; hemen &#xE7;&#xF6;zmelisin. L&#xFC;tfen acele et.
finishDlg=Lord seni bana g&#xF6;nderdi. Senden haberim var. Toplad&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n &#x15F;eyleri bana verirsen onlar&#x131; incelerim. Sonra bunlar&#x131; l&#xFC;tfen Lord'a geri g&#xF6;t&#xFC;r. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Delivery of Werefox's tail to Jaime 
desc=According to this document, there was an experiment from there. There are no detailed contents except that the experiment used human body. I think horrible things happened from the experiment. I told Jaime, so if you collect and bring Werefox's tails, Jaime will analyze the tail. 
runDlg=You should solve the incident of this dangerous cave as soon as possible. Hurry up.
finishDlg=The lord sent you to me. I heard about you. If you give me the stuff, I'll look into that. Please turn back to the lord. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10002><ad3b10003><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Werefox'un Yok edilmesi
desc=Bu yarat&#x131;k do&#x11F;al yollarla olu&#x15F;mam&#x131;&#x15F;. Bu t&#xFC;r bir yarat&#x131;k d&#xFC;nya i&#xE7;in b&#xFC;y&#xFC;k bir tehdit olu&#x15F;turabilir. Ma&#x11F;aran&#x131;n i&#xE7;inde insan v&#xFC;c&#xFC;duyla deney yap&#x131;ld&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; duydum. G&#xF6;r&#xFC;nen o ki bir insan ve bir tilki birle&#x15F;tirilmi&#x15F; ve de ortaya bu &#xE7;&#x131;km&#x131;&#x15F;. Lord bu yarat&#x131;klar&#x131;n tehlikeli oldu&#x11F;unu onaylad&#x131; ve bu olay&#x131; senin &#xE7;&#xF6;zmeni istedi. Ma&#x11F;araya git ve Werefox'lar&#x131; yok et. Hi&#xE7;bir ba&#x15F;ar&#x131;s&#x131;zl&#x131;k olmadan hepsinin temizlenmesi gerekiyor. 
runDlg=Tehlikeli yarat&#x131;klar bu d&#xFC;nyada &#xF6;ylece dola&#x15F;mamal&#x131;.
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Werefox'lar do&#x11F;al bir yolla olu&#x15F;mad&#x131;lar. Bu y&#xFC;zden yok edilmeleri gerekiyor. Kurban edilmeleri her ne kadar &#xFC;z&#xFC;c&#xFC; olsa da bunu yapmak zorunday&#x131;z.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Werefox Elimination
desc=This creature was not formed by nature. This kind of creature becomes a biggest threat to this world. I heard that there was an experiment of a human body inside the cave. Perhaps it seems that a man and fox are combined and both become one as a result. The lord confirmed how the creature is dangerous, so he requested you  handle this. Go to the cave and eliminate Werefoxes. They should be wiped out without fail. 
runDlg=The dangerous things must not go around this world.
finishDlg=Good job. The Werefoxes was not formed by nature. We would have eliminated them. Even if we are regrettable for their sacrifice.
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10003><ad3b10004><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Guard Werefox'un Silah Koleksiyonu 
desc=Sen Jamie ile konu&#x15F;urken ekstra bir rapor geldi. Ma&#x11F;aray&#x131; koruyan Werefox'lar varm&#x131;&#x15F;. Onlara Guard Werefox (Koruyucu Werefox) demeyi uygun bulduk. Ma&#x11F;arada ilerlemek i&#xE7;in onlar&#x131; yok etmemiz gerekiyor. &#xD6;ncelikle say&#x131;lar&#x131; ne olursa olsun silahlar&#x131;n&#x131; toplamal&#x131;y&#x131;z ve b&#xF6;ylece daha fazla silahlanmalar&#x131;n&#x131; &#xF6;nlemeliyiz. Ma&#x11F;aran&#x131;n i&#xE7;indeki kaynaklar s&#x131;n&#x131;rl&#x131;, bu y&#xFC;zden &#x15F;imdi gitmeli ve silahlar&#x131;n&#x131; onlardan al&#x131;p uzakla&#x15F;t&#x131;rmal&#x131;s&#x131;n. 
runDlg=Silahlar&#x131; olmadan daha da zay&#x131;f d&#xFC;&#x15F;ecekler. 
finishDlg=Werefox'lar&#x131;n g&#xFC;&#xE7;leri biraz azalm&#x131;&#x15F; g&#xF6;r&#xFC;n&#xFC;yor, &#xE7;&#xFC;nk&#xFC; silahlar&#x131;n&#x131; ald&#x131;k. Risk ma&#x11F;aran&#x131;n d&#x131;&#x15F;&#x131;na ta&#x15F;madan onlar&#x131; bask&#x131; alt&#x131;nda tutmaya devam etmeliyiz. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Guard Werefox's weapon Collection 
desc=While you talked to Jaime, we received a report in addition. There are Werefoxes who guard  the cave. We dedide to call them Guard Werefox. For advancing into the cave, we should eliminate them. At first, as collecting their weapons regardless of variation of their number, let's prevent them from being armed. The resource inside the cave is limited, so you'd better take thier weapons. 
runDlg=They'll become weak much more without weapons. 
finishDlg=Werefoxes' strength seems to weaken because we took their weopens. Before the risk comes out of the cave, we'll continue to put pressure. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10004><ad3b10005><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Guard Werefox'&#x131;n yok edilmesi 
desc=Ma&#x11F;aran&#x131;n &#xF6;n&#xFC;nde &#xE7;ok say&#x131;da koruma var, i&#xE7;eride olup bitenlerle ilgili bilgi almak bu y&#xFC;zden zor. &#x130;&#xE7;erisiyle ilgili bilgi alamad&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;m&#x131;z s&#xFC;rece d&#xFC;&#x15F;mandan gelecek s&#xFC;rpriz sald&#x131;r&#x131;lara maruz kalabiliriz. Guard Werefox'lar&#x131; g&#xF6;zlem yapmam&#x131;za engel oluyorlar. Silahlar&#x131;n&#x131; almam&#x131;za ve yok etmemize ra&#x11F;men say&#x131;lar&#x131; hala &#xE7;ok fazla. M&#xFC;mk&#xFC;n oldu&#x11F;unca &#xE7;ok say&#x131;da Guard Werefox yok etmeye &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;.
runDlg=Korumalardan kurtulduktan sonra g&#xF6;zc&#xFC;ler yollayaca&#x11F;&#x131;m. 
finishDlg=&#x15E;imdi biraz inceleme yapal&#x131;m. Biraz mola ver.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Guard Werefox elimination 
desc=Owing to too many guards in front of the cave, it is difficult to gain the inside information. Unless we find out information through reconnoitering the inside, we may have troubles for enemy's surprise attack. Guard Werefoxes are obstructing our recon. Dispite taking weapons and eliminating them, still their number is great. Eliminate Guard Werefoxes as many as possible
runDlg=After getting rid of guards, I'll make a connaissance.
finishDlg=Right now, let's reconnoiter. Take a break for a while.
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10005><ad3b10006><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Werefox'lar&#x131;n Yok edilmesi
Mission2=Guard Werefox'lar&#x131;n Yok edilmesi
desc=Sen Werefox'larla sava&#x15F;&#x131;rken ben de sana yard&#x131;mc&#x131; olman&#x131;n yollar&#x131;n&#x131; ar&#x131;yordum. Bu y&#xFC;zden senin i&#xE7;in bir &#x15F;eyler haz&#x131;rlas&#x131;nlar diye birtak&#x131;m yetenekli insanlar &#xE7;a&#x11F;&#x131;rd&#x131;m. &#x15E;imdi bunlar&#x131; yapmaya ba&#x15F;layabiliriz ve bu faydal&#x131; e&#x15F;yalarla k&#x131;sa s&#xFC;rede yola &#xE7;&#x131;kar&#x131;z. Ma&#x11F;aran&#x131;n i&#xE7;indeki tehdite kar&#x15F;&#x131; sava&#x15F; ba&#x15F;latman&#x131;n zaman&#x131;d&#x131;r. Ma&#x11F;aran&#x131;n &#xF6;n&#xFC;ndeki Werefox'lar&#x131; bir &#x15F;ekilde temizledik ancak g&#xFC;venli&#x11F;imiz yine de garanti de&#x11F;il. &#xD6;n taraftaki geri kalan t&#xFC;m Werefox'lar&#x131; yok et, sonra &#x15F;u ma&#x11F;ara sava&#x15F;&#x131;n&#x131; ba&#x15F;latal&#x131;m. 
runDlg=Haydi yava&#x15F; yava&#x15F; &#xF6;n taraftan hareket edelim. Cardiff Island'&#x131; tehdit eden her &#x15F;ey yok edilmeli.
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Ah,g&#xF6;zc&#xFC;ler de geri d&#xF6;nd&#xFC;ler. Seni yeni bilgilerden haberdar edece&#x11F;im. L&#xFC;tfen birac&#x131;k bekle. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Werefox Elimination
Mission2=Guard Werefox Elimination
desc= While you fight with Werefoxes, I was finding out the way that supports you. So I ordered skillful people to make some stuff for you. If they begin to be made from now, before long support objects will  arrive at. Now it's time to start a war against the threat inside the cave. We wiped out Werefoxes in front somewhat, but there's no guarantee for safety. Eliminate the rest of Werefoxes in front, then we can carry out the cave war.
runDlg=Go forward from the front. Things that threaten Cardiff island must be eliminated.
finishDlg=Good job. Ah, the scouts just came back. I'll let you know about new informations. Please wait for a while. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10006><ad3b10007><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Sick Huge Mole'un Yok edilmesi 
desc=Tam do&#x11F;ru zamanda geldin. Tan&#x131;&#x15F;mam&#x131;z&#x131;n &#xFC;zerinden as&#x131;rlar ge&#xE7;ti sanki. &#x130;&#x15F;imiz acil, bu y&#xFC;zden laf&#x131; doland&#x131;rmayaca&#x11F;&#x131;m. Ma&#x11F;aray&#x131; Lord'un yapt&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;ndan daha farkl&#x131; bir &#x15F;ekilde, farkl&#x131; a&#xE7;&#x131;lardan inceledim. Ma&#x11F;aran&#x131;n etraf&#x131;na &#x15F;&#xF6;yle bir bakanlar yery&#xFC;z&#xFC;nden t&#xFC;reyen tuhaf yarat&#x131;klar g&#xF6;rd&#xFC;klerini ve ke&#x15F;ifleri engellendi&#x11F;inden oradan ka&#xE7;t&#x131;klar&#x131;n&#x131; anlat&#x131;yorlar. Bu ma&#x11F;arada &#xE7;ok say&#x131;da tuhaf yarat&#x131;k var gibi. Bunlar&#x131; bana a&#xE7;&#x131;klaman&#x131; ve rapor etmeni istiyorum.
runDlg=Bu ma&#x11F;ara tehlikeli &#x15F;eylerle dolup ta&#x15F;&#x131;yor. Yine de iyi bir i&#x15F; ba&#x15F;ard&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; d&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;n&#xFC;yorum. 
finishDlg=Kim olduklar&#x131;n&#x131; bulabilir misin?  Kocaman k&#xF6;stebekler mi? &#x15E;a&#x15F;k&#x131;n durumday&#x131;m. Bu bilgiyi Lord'a rapor edece&#x11F;im. L&#xFC;tfen Lord'a git.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Sick Huge Mole Elimination 
desc=You're here at just right time. It's been ages since we met. Because of an emergency, I'll skip more greeting. I  looked into the cave in different route from the lord. People who looked into around the cave are saying that they saw strange creatures who sprang up in the earth and obstructed their reconnaissance, so they escaped with hard troubles. There seem to be many strange monsters in the cave. I want you to reveal and report who they are.
runDlg=The cave swarms with dangerous stuff. Yet I believe you make a good job. 
finishDlg=Did you know who they are? Huge moles? I am dumbfounded. I'll report the lord about this fact. Please go to the lord. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10007><ad3b10008><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Sick Huge Mole'un Yok edilmesi 
desc=Bu deneyden ka&#xE7; tane tehlikeli yarat&#x131;k t&#xFC;redi, kimbilir. &#x15E;u d&#xFC;nyada kim b&#xF6;ylesine fena &#x15F;eyler yapabilir? K&#xF6;stebekler de tilkiler de kurban edilmi&#x15F;. &#x130;nsanlar&#x131;n da bu deneyin bir par&#xE7;as&#x131; olmalar&#x131; da &#xE7;ok &#xFC;z&#xFC;c&#xFC;. Bunun bir &#xE7;&#xF6;z&#xFC;m&#xFC; yok. Yine de e&#x11F;er ihmal edilirse, bu yarat&#x131;klar bir g&#xFC;n Roxbury i&#xE7;in tehdit olu&#x15F;turabilirler. Senden ma&#x11F;araya gitmeni ve t&#xFC;m Sick Huge Mole'lardan kurtulman&#x131; istiyorum. 
runDlg=Bu deneyin sonu&#xE7;lar&#x131; gittik&#xE7;e daha da korkun&#xE7;la&#x15F;&#x131;yor. Hen&#xFC;z bilmedi&#x11F;imiz &#x15F;eylere kar&#x15F;&#x131; kendini haz&#x131;rla.
finishDlg=K&#xF6;stebekler yeralt&#x131;nda ya&#x15F;ar... Yery&#xFC;z&#xFC;nde &#xE7;ok say&#x131;da k&#xF6;stebek olmal&#x131;. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Sick Huge Mole Elimination 
desc=We don't know how many dangerous creatures are sacrificed by experiment. Who committed such horrible things? Moles as well as foxes are sacrified. It's also regrettable that People were sacrificed by experiment. Yet it can't be helped. But if neglected, the creatures will become a threat to Roxbury one day. I want you to go to the cave and get rid of all Sick Huge Moles. 
runDlg=The result of the experiment gradually becomes a horrible reality. Steel yourself for any thing we don't know yet. 
finishDlg=Some moles come in and out the earth&#x2026;there may be many moles in the earth. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10008><ad3b10009><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=The essence of unstable earth Toplama
desc=Yery&#xFC;z&#xFC;n&#xFC;n ruhunun sesini duydum. Ma&#x11F;arada ya&#x15F;ayan Weremole'lar yery&#xFC;z&#xFC;n&#xFC; kaz&#x131;yorlar, bu y&#xFC;zden de yery&#xFC;z&#xFC;ndeki ruhlar ve yarat&#x131;klar korkuyor. Sick Huge Mole'un varl&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; pek &#xE7;ok ruhu rahats&#x131;z ediyor. Senden onlara yard&#x131;m etmeni istiyorum, bu sayede yeniden huzura kavu&#x15F;abilirler. Bunu, yani her ruhu temsil eden bu kolyeyi ta&#x15F;&#x131;. Weremole'lar&#x131; yok etti&#x11F;inde bu, Essence of Enstable Earth'&#xFC; ele ge&#xF6;irmeni sa&#x11F;layacakt&#x131;r. L&#xFC;tfen o &#xF6;zle bana geri gel. 
runDlg=Do&#x11F;adaki yarat&#x131;klar i&#xE7;in zararl&#x131; olduklar&#x131;ndan onlar&#x131; hemen yok etmelisin. Ruhlar i&#xE7;in en b&#xFC;y&#xFC;k tehdidi onlar olu&#x15F;turuyorlar. 
finishDlg=Cardiff Island'daki ruhlar huzur i&#xE7;inde olsunlar... Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=The essence of unstable earth Collection
desc=I heard a voice from the spirit of the earth. Weremoles who lived in the cave are coming in and out the earth, so creatures and spirits in the earth are afraid of the thing. On account of Sick Huge Mole's existence, spirits are nervous. I want you to help them so that they find their peace again. Carry this, earth spirit's pendant. When you eliminate Weremoles, this will help that you gain the essence of unstable earth. Please come to me with the essence. 
runDlg=Because they are injurious to creatures in nature, you should get rid of them quickly. They are the most threatening existence to spirits. 
finishDlg=May the peace be always with spirits in Cardiff island&#x2026;thank you.
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10009><ad3b10010><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Whisman Ghoul'un Yok edilmesi
desc=Sen weremole'lar&#x131; yok etmekle me&#x15F;gulken biz de incelemelre devam ettik ve korkun&#xE7; bir rapor ald&#x131;m. V&#xFC;cutlar&#x131; deneyde kullan&#x131;lan insanlar &#xF6;lm&#xFC;&#x15F; olmas&#x131;na ra&#x11F;men ya&#x15F;ayan canl&#x131;lar gibi hareket etmeye devam ediyorlar. Ma&#x11F;arada hem &#xF6;l&#xFC; olan ama bir yandan da ya&#x15F;amaya devam eden &#x15F;eyler var. Korkunu yen ve  Whisman Ghoul'lar&#x131; yok et. 
runDlg=Noble Masquer 'in bu deneyi insan v&#xFC;cudu &#xFC;zerinde yapt&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;na inanam&#x131;yorum.
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Haydi s&#x131;radaki g&#xF6;reve ge&#xE7;elim.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Whisman Ghoul Elimination
desc=While you eliminate the weremoles, we continued to reconnoiter. After reconnaissance, I got a terrible report. Even though the people who had been used for body experiment died, they are moving around like living things. It's really terrible. Both no living and no dead things go around the cave. Conquer your fear and eliminate Whisman Ghouls. 
runDlg=I can't believe Noble Masquer made the experiment on a human body.
finishDlg=Good job. Let's continue to proceed to the next.
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10010><ad3b10011><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Hagdis Zombie'nin Yok edilmesi
desc=&#x130;&#xE7;eri do&#x11F;ru ilerledik&#xE7;e ma&#x11F;aran&#x131;n tehlikesi de art&#x131;yor. &#x130;nsanlar &#xFC;zerinde nas&#x131;l bir deney yapt&#x131;lar ki b&#xF6;yle bir sonu&#xE7; &#xE7;&#x131;kt&#x131; bilemiyorum. Yine de bu i&#x15F;in hemen bitirilmesi gerekiyor. Gece g&#xFC;nd&#xFC;z &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F; ve bunlar&#x131; k&#xF6;kten temizle. Bu konuda bir tek sana g&#xFC;veniyorum.
runDlg=Ne kadar da kasvetli bir &#x15F;afak vakti! Ya&#x15F;ayan &#xD6;l&#xFC;ler i&#xE7;in....
finishDlg=Bu tehlikeli i&#x15F;in &#xFC;stesinden gelmeyi ba&#x15F;ard&#x131;n. Jamie'den bir iyilik istedim. Bir kez Jamie'ye git. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hagdis Zombie Elimination 
desc=The more we go into, the more dangerous is this cave. I don't know if they changed in this way by what influence of human experiment. But this job should be finished quickly. Make an effort day and night until all these things are wiped out. I only believe you.
runDlg=What a groomy dawn! Living corpses are&#x2026;.
finishDlg=You did dangerous things well. I asked a favor to Jaime. Go to Jaime at once. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10011><ad3b10012><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Whisman Ghoul'un  kemiklerini toplama 
Mission2=Whisman Ghoul'un  kemiklerini toplama 
desc=Bunlar ya&#x15F;ayan &#xF6;l&#xFC;ler. Beyinleri &#xF6;lm&#xFC;&#x15F;, ruhlar&#x131; gitmi&#x15F; ama bedenleri hala canl&#x131;. Bu deneyin ba&#x15F;&#x131;nda kimin oldu&#x11F;unu a&#xE7;&#x131;klamay&#x131;z. B&#xF6;ylece onlar&#x131; yeniden do&#x11F;aya kavu&#x15F;turabiliriz. Whisman Ghoul ve Whisman Zombie'yi yok et ve kemiklerini topla. Buna neden olanlar&#x131; a&#xE7;&#x131;&#x11F;a &#xE7;&#x131;karmak i&#xE7;in elimden geleni yapaca&#x11F;&#x131;m. 
runDlg=Bu cesetlerin hala hareket ediyor olmas&#x131; &#xE7;ok korkun&#xE7;. 
finishDlg=&#xC7;aba g&#xF6;sterdi&#x11F;in i&#xE7;in te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler. Ruhlar&#x131;n sesine kulak verelim ve t&#xFC;m bunlar&#x131;n sebebini ke&#x15F;fedelim. Lord seni &#xE7;a&#x11F;&#x131;r&#x131;yor. Git ve onu bul.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Whisman Ghoul's  bone collection 
Mission2=Whisman Ghoul's bone collection 
desc=The things are living corpses. Their brain and spirit already died but body is alive. We should reveal who is the real supervisor of this experiment. Then we can turn back to nature. Eliminate Whisman Ghoul and Whisman Ghoul Zombie and collect their bones. With a great effort, I'll uncover the cause. 
runDlg=Corpses go around? It's horrible. 
finishDlg=Thank you for your effort. Let's discover the cause through spirit's voice. The lord calls out you. Go to him.
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10012><ad3b10013><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Hagdis Ghoul'un Yok edilmesi 
desc=Whisman cesetlerinin yan&#x131; s&#x131;ra ba&#x15F;ka &#xE7;e&#x15F;it cesetler de bulundu. Hagdis kabilesinin cesetleri de canl&#x131; canl&#x131; dolan&#x131;yorlar. Deney sonucu ortaya &#xE7;&#x131;kan bu cesetlerin say&#x131;s&#x131; az de&#x11F;il. Bu korkun&#xE7; cesetleri temizlemelisin. &#x15E;imdi ma&#x11F;araya git ve Hagdis Ghoul'lar&#x131; yok et. 
runDlg=Hagdis Ghoul da tehlikelidir. L&#xFC;tfen kendine dikkat et.
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. G&#xF6;r&#xFC;nen o ki bu ma&#x11F;ara i&#x15F;inin sonuna geldik. Biraz daha &#xE7;aba g&#xF6;sterirsek iyi bir sonu&#xE7; alabiliriz. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hagdis Ghoul Elimination 
desc=Another kind of corpses were found besides Whisman corpses. Hagdis tribe's corpses also are going around alive. Corpses made by experiment is no small number. You should wipe out the horrible corpses. Right now go to the cave and get rid of Hagdis Ghouls. 
runDlg=Hagdis Ghoul is also dangerous. Please take care of yourself.
finishDlg=Good job. Likely to come to the end of this cave now. With a little extra effort, we'll make a result. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10013><ad3b10014><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Hagdis Zombie'nin Yok edilmesi 
desc=Jaime'nin s&#xF6;yledi&#x11F;ine g&#xF6;re hortlak ve zombi gruplar&#x131;n&#x131;n ard&#x131;nda g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC; bir b&#xFC;y&#xFC;c&#xFC; yer al&#x131;yormu&#x15F;. Onun kim oldu&#x11F;unu hen&#xFC;z bilmiyoruz. Ancak biraz daha ara&#x15F;t&#x131;rmayla Jamie'den bunu &#xF6;&#x11F;renebiliriz. Hagdis Zombie'lerini ve Hagdis Ghoul'lar&#x131;n&#x131; yok etmelisin. Daha rahat bir ara&#x15F;t&#x131;rma yapabilmemiz i&#xE7;in &#xF6;ncelikle Hagdis Zombie'lerini yok et. 
runDlg=Bu ma&#x11F;aran&#x131;n sonu g&#xF6;r&#xFC;n&#xFC;yor. Tehlikeli Hadgis Zombie'leri yok edildi&#x11F;inde ke&#x15F;if daha kolay olacakt&#x131;r. 
finishDlg=&#x15E;imdi, Jamie'nin ara&#x15F;t&#x131;rmas&#x131;ndan bir sonu&#xE7; &#xE7;&#x131;kt&#x131;. Jamie'ye git.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hagdis Zombie Elimination 
desc=Jaime said that there is a powerful wizard in the back of ghoul and zombie group. We don't know yet who he is, but we'll come to know, by Jaime, after a bit more of investigation. You have to eliminate Hagdis Zombies as well as Hagdis Ghouls. Eliminate Hagdis Zombies for convient investigation. 
runDlg=The end of this cave seems to be seen. Exploration will be easier as eliminating the dangerous Hagdis Zombies. 
finishDlg=Now, there is a result  about Jaime's investigation. Go to Jaime.
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10014><ad3b10015><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Hagdis Ghoul'un Kemiklerinin Toplanmas&#x131; 
Mission2=Hagdis Zombie'un Kemiklerinin Toplanmas&#x131; 
desc=Bana getirdi&#x11F;in kemikler arac&#x131;l&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;yla hangi deneyin yap&#x131;ld&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; ve nas&#x131;l sonu&#xE7;lar do&#x11F;urdu&#x11F;unu buldum. Bu deneyi y&#xF6;neten B&#xFC;y&#xFC;c&#xFC; &#xE7;ok uzun zaman &#xF6;nce &#xF6;lm&#xFC;&#x15F;. Ama hala ya&#x15F;&#x131;yormu&#x15F; gibi g&#xF6;r&#xFC;n&#xFC;yor. Black Wizard ad&#x131; verilen ki&#x15F;inin v&#xFC;cutlar &#xFC;zerinde deney yapt&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; anla&#x15F;&#x131;l&#x131;yor. Noble Masquer grubundaki deney y&#xFC;z&#xFC;nden Black Wizard s&#xFC;rg&#xFC;ne g&#xF6;nderilmi&#x15F;. &#x15E;imdilerde  Cardiff Island'da kal&#x131;yor. Ama canl&#x131; canl&#x131; g&#xF6;m&#xFC;ld&#xFC;&#x11F;&#xFC; halde neden &#xF6;l&#xFC; olmad&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; hala anlayam&#x131;yorum. Ma&#x11F;araya tekrar git ve Hagdis Ghoul ve Hagdis Zombie'nin kemiklerini getir. Bunlar&#x131; ara&#x15F;t&#x131;r&#x131;rsak hala nas&#x131;l hayatta olabildi&#x11F;ini de &#xE7;&#xF6;zebiliriz.
runDlg=Bu &#xE7;ok &#x15F;a&#x15F;&#x131;rt&#x131;c&#x131;. Hala ya&#x15F;&#x131;yor! 
finishDlg=Hepsini getirdin. K&#x131;sa bir ara&#x15F;t&#x131;rma yapaca&#x11F;&#x131;m. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hagdis Ghoul's Bone collection 
Mission2=Hagdis Zombie's Bone Collection 
desc=Through the bone you had given me, I found which experiment  it is and which result was formed. Wizard who had carried out the experiment died a long time ago. But as for this result, he seems to be still alive. It is thought that who called Black Wizard, had done body experiment. Because of the experiment in the group of Noble Masquer, Black Wizard was exiled. Now he is staying in Cardiff island. But I am wondering how he can't be dead, despite being buried alive. Go to the cave again and bring Hagdis Ghoul and Hagdis Zombie's bones. Through investigation of them, we confirm how to be alive.
runDlg=It's surprising. He has lived till now! 
finishDlg=You bring them very well. I'll look into them for a while. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10015><ad3b10016><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Lord Lionel ile sohbet
desc=Aman Tanr&#x131;m! &#xC7;ok korkun&#xE7;. Black Wizard kendisini d&#xF6;n&#xFC;&#x15F;t&#xFC;rmi&#x15F; ve Lich olmu&#x15F;. G&#xF6;m&#xFC;ld&#xFC;&#x11F;&#xFC; s&#x131;rada ka&#xE7;maya &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;&#x131;rken deneyde kulland&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; bir &#x15F;eyi yemi&#x15F; olmal&#x131;. Bu bilgiyi Lord'a rapor et. 
runDlg=Bu cidden &#xE7;ok tehlikeli. Do&#x11F;rudan Lord'a git. 
finishDlg=Ne? Black Wizard Lich'e d&#xF6;n&#xFC;&#x15F;m&#xFC;&#x15F; ve de hala hayatta m&#x131;? Black Wizard hayatta m&#x131;! &#xD6;nce bu konuda Roderick'e dan&#x131;&#x15F;aca&#x11F;&#x131;m. Black Wizard'&#x131; yok etmek i&#xE7;in hemen haz&#x131;rlan. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conservation with Sir Raionel
desc=My god! It's terrible. Black Wizard changed himself into Lich. While being buried and trying to escape, probably he ate something he experimented. Report this fact to the lord. 
runDlg=It's a dangerous thing. Go ahead to the lord. 
finishDlg=What? Did you say Black Wizard turned into Leach and still alive?  Black Wizard is alive yet! At first I'll consult Roderick about this. Prepare for Black Wizard's elimination right now. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10016><ad3b10017><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Black Wizard'&#x131;n Yok edilmesi 
desc=Roderick'in dedi&#x11F;ine g&#xF6;re ge&#xE7;mi&#x15F;te insan bedeni &#xFC;zerinde deneyler yapt&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; i&#xE7;in s&#xFC;rg&#xFC;ne g&#xF6;nderilmi&#x15F;. Affedilemez bir deney! &#x130;&#x15F;te bir grubun Black Wizard'&#x131; getirip canl&#x131; canl&#x131; g&#xF6;md&#xFC;&#x11F;&#xFC; nokta buras&#x131;. Art&#x131;k bu &#xE7;ok uzun zamand&#x131;r devam eden laneti sona erdirmenin vaktidir. Haydi git ve Black Wizard'&#x131; yok et. 
runDlg=Sana iyi &#x15F;anslar diliyorum. 
finishDlg=Roderick ve ben bu meseleyi halledece&#x11F;iz. K&#xF6;yl&#xFC;ler d&#x131;&#x15F;&#x131;nda kimsenin bu olaydan haberdar olmamas&#x131; &#xE7;ok rahatlat&#x131;c&#x131;. Di&#x11F;er k&#xF6;yl&#xFC;ler duymas&#x131;nlar, sana bu konuda g&#xFC;veniyorum. Bu b&#xFC;y&#xFC;k ba&#x15F;ar&#x131;ndan &#xF6;t&#xFC;r&#xFC; sana b&#xFC;y&#xFC;k bir &#xF6;d&#xFC;l verece&#x11F;im. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Black Wizard Elimination 
desc=Roderick says that he was exiled because of carrying out the experiment on a human body in the past. How unpardonable experiment it is! Here is the spot which a group with Black Wizard was exiled. Now we should finish this long, long curse. Go get rid of Black Wizard. 
runDlg=I wish you good luck. 
finishDlg=Roderick and I'll settle this incident. It's a relieve that people besides this villagers don't still know. I wish you too don't say this thing in other village. I'll give a great reward for your great achievement. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10017><ad3b10018><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Sick Huge Mole'un Yok edilmesi 
desc=Ara&#x15F;t&#x131;rmalar&#x131;ma g&#xF6;re bu k&#xF6;stebeklerin iyile&#x15F;tirilmeleri gerekiyor. Ruhlara daha &#xF6;nce bu k&#xF6;stebeklerle ilgili sorular somu&#x15F;tum. O zamanlarda sadece tehlikeli olduklar&#x131;n&#x131; d&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;n&#xFC;yordum. Ama &#x15F;imdi hasta olduklar&#x131; i&#xE7;in b&#xF6;yle &#x15F;eylerin oldu&#x11F;unu biliyorum. Sana bu ta&#x15F;&#x131; verece&#x11F;im. Buna 'do&#x11F;al g&#xFC;&#xE7;ler' deniyor. Hasta yarat&#x131;klar&#x131; iyile&#x15F;tirme yetene&#x11F;i var. K&#xF6;stebekleri yok edersen bu ta&#x15F; onlar&#x131;n do&#x11F;aya geri d&#xF6;nmelerini sa&#x11F;layacak. 
runDlg=Bu hasta hayvanlar&#x131; do&#x11F;an&#x131;n merkezine g&#xF6;t&#xFC;rebilesin...
finishDlg=&#xC7;ok zor bir i&#x15F;in alt&#x131;ndan ba&#x15F;ar&#x131;yla kalkt&#x131;n. Bir kez daha zavall&#x131; hayvanlar&#x131; do&#x11F;al ortamlar&#x131;na kavu&#x15F;turdun. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Sick Huge Mole Elimination 
desc= On my investigation, these moles need to be treated. I have ever asked spirits about these moles before, that time I thought they only were dangerous. But now I know that because they were sick, such things happened.  I'll give this. This stone called 'natural forces' has an ability that is able to heal sick creatures. If you eliminate the moles, this stone will send back them to nature. 
runDlg=May you return sick animals to the bosom of nature...
finishDlg=You performed a difficult job well. Once more you turned back the poor animals to nature. 
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10018><ad3b10019><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Whisman Zombie'nin Yok edilmesi 
Mission2=Hagdis Zombie'nin Yok edilmesi 
desc=Bize yard&#x131;mc&#x131; olman gereken bir konu daha var. Ma&#x11F;aradaki zombie'ler sald&#x131;r&#x131;m&#x131;za kar&#x15F;&#x131;l&#x131;k vermeye ba&#x15F;lad&#x131;lar. Yetenekli de&#x11F;iller ancak iyi sald&#x131;r&#x131;yorlar. Git ve bu Zombie'leri yok et. 
runDlg=Zombie'leri yok etmeni emrediyorum. Ma&#x11F;aradaki t&#xFC;m Zombie'leri temizle. 
finishDlg=Bundan sonra Zombie sald&#x131;r&#x131;s&#x131; olmayaca&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; d&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;n&#xFC;yorum. Bir g&#xF6;rev daha var, l&#xFC;tfen biraz bekle.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Whisman Zombie Elimination 
Mission2=Hagdis Zombie Elimination 
desc=There is one thing you have to help. Zombies in the cave begin to attack us against our attack. They have no intelligence, but they continue to attack intelligently. Go ahead and get rid of Zombies. 
runDlg=I order you to wipe out Zombie. Clean up all the Zombies in the cave. 
finishDlg=I believe there seems to be no Zombie's attack any more. You have a next mission, please wait for a while.
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10019><ad3b10020><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Whisman Ghoul'un Yok edilmesi 
Mission2=Hagdis Ghoul'un Yok edilmesi 
desc=Bize Zombie'lerle birlikte sald&#x131;ran bir ba&#x15F;ka grup daha vard&#x131;. &#x130;simleri Ghoul. Sadece &#xE7;&#xFC;r&#xFC;k etten ve kemikten ibaretler ama insanlara fena sald&#x131;r&#x131;yorlar. Onlardan korkman gerekmiyor. Pek &#xE7;ok b&#xFC;y&#xFC;k zorlu&#x11F;un &#xFC;stesinden gelmedin mi sen? Git ve bu Ghoul'leri yok et. Bu lanetli yeri m&#xFC;h&#xFC;rlemenin vakti geldi.
runDlg=Ghoul'leri yok ettin mi? Hadi can&#x131;m, bu g&#xF6;revden sonra biraz dinlenmek istemiyor musun? 
finishDlg=Ghoul'leri ba&#x15F;ar&#x131;l&#x131; bir &#x15F;ekilde yok ettin. Yeni g&#xF6;revine &#xE7;&#x131;kmadan &#xF6;nce biraz dinlen.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Whisman Ghoul Elimination 
Mission2=Hagdis Ghoul Elimination 
desc=There was another group who have attacked us with Zombie. Their name is Ghoul. Only pieces of rotten meat and bones hit people with terror. But you don't need to be afraid of them. Are you the veteran who has overcome many difficulty? Go eliminate Ghouls. It is the time when we should seal this curse place.
runDlg=Did you eliminate Ghouls? Don't you want to take a rest after this job? 
finishDlg=You eliminated Ghouls very well. Take a rest and carry out next mission.
</newversion></questtextxml></ad3b10020></diff><settings><searchkey> questlistid</searchkey><ignore> id</ignore><columnnametable> </columnnametable><parsexml> </parsexml></settings></server_questtext_TR></number69></sql></Cache>
